'''克里斯汀·查爾斯·菲利普·貝爾'''（{{lang-en|Christian Charles Philip Bale}}，{{bd|1974年|1月30日}}）是英國男演員。貝爾以多變且反覆無常的身材變化來飾演角色而聞名，並一直是多類電影的男主角。他{{tsl|en|List of awards and nominations received by Christian Bale|克里斯汀·貝爾獲獎與提名列表|獲獎無數}}，先後奪得一次[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]2010年最佳男配角獎和兩次[[金球獎|金球獎]]。2011年，《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]》將其評為[[時代百大人物|最具影響力的一百人]]。

貝爾出身[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]的英國家庭，13歲初涉影壇就主演[[斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格|斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格]]的戰爭片《[[太陽帝國_(電影)|太陽帝國]]》。經過十多年的主配角演出，他在黑色喜劇《[[美色殺人狂|美色殺人狂]]》和心理驚悚片《[[克里斯汀貝爾之黑暗時刻|-{zh-hans:机械师; zh-hk:迷魂殺陣; zh-tw:克里斯汀貝爾之黑暗時刻;}-]]》的演出引起更廣泛的關注。貝爾後來在《[[蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻]]》、《[[黑暗騎士|黑暗騎士]]》和《[[黑暗騎士：黎明昇起|黑暗騎士：黎明昇起]]》扮演的[[蝙蝠俠|蝙蝠俠]]獲得一致好評，此三部曲更列入最賣座系列電影。

除蝙蝠俠外，貝爾持續主演其他電影作品，包括時代片《[[頂尖對決|頂尖對決]]》、動作片《[[魔鬼終結者：未來救贖|魔鬼終結者：未來救贖]]》、犯罪片《[[頭號公敵|頭號公敵]]》、史詩片《[[出埃及記：天地王者|出埃及記：天地王者]]》和歷史片《{{tsl|en|The Promise|愛在戰火紛飛時|-{zh-cn:承诺; zh-tw:愛在戰火紛飛時;}-}}》。貝爾因2010年傳記片《[[燃燒鬥魂|-{zh-hans:斗士; zh-tw:燃燒鬥魂; zh-hk:擊情手足;}-]]》奪得奧斯卡金像獎和金球獎。隨後幾年，他還因《[[美国骗局|美国骗局]]》、《[[大賣空_(電影)|-{zh-tw:大賣空;zh-cn:大空头;zh-hk:沽注一擲;}-]]》和《[[為副不仁|為副不仁]]》入圍更多奧斯卡金像獎和金球獎。貝爾在《為副不仁》飾演政治家[[迪克·切尼|迪克·切尼]]和在運動片《[[賽道狂人|賽道狂人]]》飾演賽車手[[肯·迈尔斯_(赛车运动员)|肯·迈尔斯]]分別為他拿下第二座和入圍第五次金球獎。

==早年經歷==
1974年1月30日，克里斯汀·查爾斯·菲利普·貝爾<ref name="fullname">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thecut.com/2019/01/christian-bale-welsh-accent-golden-globes-2019.html|title=Christian Bale's Accent Is Always a Shock|date=2019-01-06|access-date=2021-04-30|website=The Cut|last=Ceròn|first=Ella|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112035646/https://www.thecut.com/2019/01/christian-bale-welsh-accent-golden-globes-2019.html|archive-date=2020-11-12|url-status=live}}</ref>在[[威爾斯|威爾斯]][[哈弗福韦斯特|哈弗福韦斯特]]的一家英國家庭出生。父親{{tsl|en|David Bale|大衛·貝爾 (企業家)|大衛·貝爾}}是企業家和活動家，母親珍妮·詹姆斯（{{lang|en|Jenny James}}）是馬戲演員<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://apnews.com/article/celebrity-birthdays-beth-hart-ray-stevens-hip-hop-and-rap-nastassja-kinski-25346e8a89639f8fd7b919440e1e9156|title=Celebrity birthdays for the week of Jan. 24-30|date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-04-30|publisher=[[美聯社|Associated Press]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120043710/https://www.apnews.com/article/celebrity-birthdays-beth-hart-ray-stevens-hip-hop-and-rap-nastassja-kinski-25346e8a89639f8fd7b919440e1e9156|archive-date=2021-01-20|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.harpersbazaar.com/uk/awards-season/a25773141/christian-bale-accent-golden-globes/|title=Christian Bale surprises the world with his British accent|work=[[時尚芭莎|Harper's Bazaar UK]]|date=2019-01-07|access-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519075757/https://www.harpersbazaar.com/uk/awards-season/a25773141/christian-bale-accent-golden-globes/|archive-date=2021-05-19|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="family">{{cite web|last1=Francis|first1=Damien|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2008/jul/22/christian.bale|title=Batman star Christian Bale arrested|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2008-07-22|access-date=2021-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126145856/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2008/jul/22/christian.bale|archive-date=2021-01-26|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾曾說：「我雖在威爾斯出生，但我不是威爾斯人，而是英國人<ref>{{cite web|last1=Butler|first1=Tom|url=https://uk.movies.yahoo.com/christian-bales-accent-is-seriously-confusing-people-in-the-first-le-mans-66-trailer-144026897.html|title=Christian Bale's accent is seriously confusing people in the first 'Le Mans '66' trailer|publisher=Yahoo! Movies|date=2019-06-03|access-date=2021-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205063552/https://uk.movies.yahoo.com/christian-bales-accent-is-seriously-confusing-people-in-the-first-le-mans-66-trailer-144026897.html|archive-date=2020-12-05|url-status=live}}</ref>。」家中還有姐姐莎朗（{{lang|en|Sharon}}）、路易絲（{{lang|en|Louise}}）和父親首段婚姻所生的同父異母姐姐艾琳（{{lang|en|Erin}}）<ref name="family"/>。貝爾祖父是[[棟篤笑|-{zh-hk:棟篤笑;zh-cn:单口喜剧;zh-tw:獨角喜劇;}-]]演員，另一名則是[[約翰·韋恩|約翰·韋恩]]的替身<ref name="intensity">{{cite news|last1=Hiscock|first1=John|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/starsandstories/8271873/Christian-Bale-Yes-it-is-the-same-guy.html|title=Christian Bale: Yes, it is the same guy|access-date=2014-02-09|date=2011-01-21|work=[[每日電訊報|The Daily Telegraph]]|archive-date=2011-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110123051635/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/starsandstories/8271873/Christian-Bale-Yes-it-is-the-same-guy.html|url-status=live}}</ref>。一家人在貝爾兩歲時離開威爾斯<ref name="abcnews">{{cite web|last1=Fisher|first1=Luchina|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/story?id=5440296&page=1|title=Big Tent Childhood: Growing up in the Circus|publisher=[[ABC新聞|ABC News]]|date=2008-07-27|access-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027102601/https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/story?id=5440296&page=1|archive-date=2020-10-27|url-status=live}}</ref>，輾轉住在[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]和英國[[牛津郡|牛津郡]]後，最後定居[[伯恩茅斯|-{zh-cn:伯恩茅斯;zh-tw:伯恩茅斯;zh-hk:般尼茅夫}-]]<ref name="darkallegation">{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/2445620/Batman-actor-Christian-Bale-released-after-assault-allegation-arrest.html|title=Batman actor Christian Bale released after assault allegation arrest|date=2008-07-22|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[每日電訊報|The Daily Telegraph]]|last1=Irvine|first1=Chris|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909163809/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/2445620/Batman-actor-Christian-Bale-released-after-assault-allegation-arrest.html|archive-date=2019-09-09|url-status=live|last2=Edwards|first2=Richard}}</ref>。貝爾表示15歲時家人已在15座城鎮生活，還稱經常搬遷是出自「需要而非選擇」，並承認這對他的職業選擇有重大影響<ref name="abcnews"/><ref name="private">{{cite web|last1=Heaf|first1=Jonathan|url=https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/article/gq-film-christian-bale-interview|title=Christian Bale on suffering from insomnia and running into Viggo Mortensen in Rome|work=[[GQ|British GQ]]|date=2012-07-23|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160923170846/https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/article/gq-film-christian-bale-interview|archive-date=2016-09-23|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Black|first1=Johnny|title=Christian Bale: 20 Things You (Probably) Don't Know About the 'Out of the Furnace' Star|url=http://lotr.moviefone.com/2013/12/06/christian-bale-facts/|access-date=2016-02-03|publisher=Moviefone|date=2013-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307053909/https://lotr.moviefone.com/2013/12/06/christian-bale-facts/|archive-date=2016-03-07|url-status=dead}}</ref>。他進入{{tsl|en|Bournemouth School|伯恩茅斯學校|-{zh-cn:伯恩茅斯;zh-tw:伯恩茅斯;zh-hk:般尼茅夫}-學校}}學習，但16歲時輟學<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/dorset/content/articles/2004/10/13/celebrities_feature.shtml|title=Dorset celebrities|publisher=[[BBC新聞|BBC News]]|date=2014-09-24|access-date=2021-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416030312/http://www.bbc.co.uk/dorset/content/articles/2004/10/13/celebrities_feature.shtml|archive-date=2021-04-16|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="plays">{{cite web|last1=Riley|first1=Jenelle|title=Christian Bale: Reluctant Movie Star Talks 'Furnace', 'Hustle'|url=https://variety.com/2013/biz/news/christian-bale-reluctant-movie-star-talks-furnace-hustle-1200884247|access-date=2021-06-05|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2013-11-26|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731171240/https://variety.com/2013/biz/news/christian-bale-reluctant-movie-star-talks-furnace-hustle-1200884247/|url-status=live}}</ref>。1991年，父母在貝爾17歲時離婚，他跟著路易絲和父親搬到洛杉磯<ref>{{cite web|last1=Blunden|first1=Mark|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/hp/front/christian-bale-s-sister-says-actor-needs-help-to-deal-with-temper-6852619.html|title=Christian Bale's sister says actor needs help to deal with temper|work=Evening Standard|date=2012-04-13|access-date=2021-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608104718/https://www.standard.co.uk/hp/front/christian-bale-s-sister-says-actor-needs-help-to-deal-with-temper-6852619.html|archive-date=2021-06-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。

貝爾兒時就練習[[芭蕾舞|芭蕾舞]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Burns|first1=Judith|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-40138653|title=Sporting plan to boost boys in ballet|publisher=[[BBC新聞|BBC News]]|date=2017-06-03|access-date=2021-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190121131803/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-40138653|archive-date=2019-01-21|url-status=live}}</ref>。年僅8歲的他在織物柔軟劑[[當妮_(寶潔公司旗下品牌)|蘭諾]]廣告首度飾演角色<ref name="first">{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/jan/04/christian-bale-i-was-asked-to-do-a-romantic-comedy-i-thought-theyd-lost-their-minds|title=Christian Bale: 'I was asked to do a romantic comedy. I thought they'd lost their minds'|date=2018-01-05|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|last=Carroll|first=Rory|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420135646/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/jan/04/christian-bale-i-was-asked-to-do-a-romantic-comedy-i-thought-theyd-lost-their-minds|archive-date=2021-04-20|url-status=live}}</ref>，還在「[[吃豆人|-{zh-cn:吃豆人;zh-hk:食鬼;zh-tw:小精靈;zh-sg:派克曼}-]]」麥片廣告亮相<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.avclub.com/a-brief-history-of-video-game-cereals-and-their-ridicul-1798251864|title=A brief history of video game cereals and their ridiculous commercials|date=2016-09-08|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[影音俱樂部|The A.V. Club]]|last=Gerardi|first=Matt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209171033/https://news.avclub.com/a-brief-history-of-video-game-cereals-and-their-ridicul-1798251864|archive-date=2021-02-09|url-status=live}}</ref>。姐姐在[[西區劇院|西區劇院]]出演[[音樂劇|音樂劇]]後，貝爾開始考慮從事專業表演<ref>{{cite web|last1=Yarrow|first1=Andrew L.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1987/12/16/movies/boy-in-empire-calls-acting-really-good-fun.html|title=Boy In 'Empire' Calls Acting 'Really Good Fun'|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1987-12-16|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723133333/https://www.nytimes.com/1987/12/16/movies/boy-in-empire-calls-acting-really-good-fun.html|archive-date=2020-07-23|url-status=live}}</ref>。他後來表示不覺得演戲有多吸引，而是應周圍人要求去做，自己也沒有原因拒絕<ref name="thr">{{cite web|last1=Feinberg|first1=Scott|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/furnace-star-christian-bale-his-658087/|title='Out of the Furnace' Star Christian Bale on His 'Love-Hate' Relationship with Acting (Q&A)|website=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2013-12-07|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518160309/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/furnace-star-christian-bale-his-658087/|archive-date=2021-05-18|url-status=live}}</ref>。參與學校劇作後，貝爾於1984年在西區劇院與[[羅溫·艾金森|羅溫·艾金森]]共演《{{tsl|en|The Nerd (play)|蠢蛋 (話劇)|蠢蛋}}》<ref name="plays"/><ref name="first"/>，他此前沒有接受任何正規表演訓練<ref name="plays"/>。

==事業==
===起步和突破（1986至1999年）===
1986年，年僅10歲的貝爾決定成為演員後在電視電影《{{tsl|en|Anastasia: The Mystery of Anna|安娜之谜}}》獲得個小角色。影片主演、[[史提芬·史匹堡|史提芬·史匹堡]]前妻{{tsl|en|Amy Irving|艾米·欧文|-{zh-hans:艾米·欧文;zh-tw:艾美·歐文;}-}}隨後向-{zh-cn:斯皮尔伯格;zh-hk:史匹堡;zh-tw:史匹柏;}-力薦貝爾出演1987年電影《[[太陽帝國_(電影)|太陽帝國]]》<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lewis|first1=Andy|last2=Anderman|first2=Maya|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/discovered-by-spielberg-a-lucky-891580/|title=Discovered by Spielberg: How a Lucky Encounter With the Director Launched These 6 Stars|website=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-05-06|access-date=2021-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608055048/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/discovered-by-spielberg-a-lucky-891580/|archive-date=2021-06-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。13歲的貝爾選角時扮演在[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]日本拘留營的英國小男孩，之後在4000名演員中脫穎而出<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://people.com/tbd/5-things-you-gotta-know-about-christian-bale/|title=5 Things You Gotta Know About Christian Bale|date=2004-10-20|access-date=2021-04-30|website=People|last=Kappes|first=Serena|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000821/https://people.com/tbd/5-things-you-gotta-know-about-christian-bale/|archive-date=2020-11-12|url-status=live}}</ref>，甚至在電影中不需口條教練就能說出上流社會的腔調<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sanello|first1=Frank|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1987-12-20-8704040617-story.html|title=Christian Bale: Spielberg's Newest Child Star|work=[[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]]|date=1987-12-20|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://archive.today/20210611042835/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1987-12-20-8704040617-story.html|archive-date=2021-06-11|url-status=live}}</ref>。這個角色讓貝爾聲名鵲起<ref name="fame">{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/dec/09/christian-bale-american-hustle-acting|title=Christian Bale: pressure as a child formed 'love/hate' relationship with acting|date=2013-12-09|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|last=Child|first=Ben|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009211437/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/dec/09/christian-bale-american-hustle-acting|archive-date=2015-10-09|url-status=live}}</ref>，電影也令他廣受讚譽，更贏得[[國家評論協會|國家評論協會]]首次頒發的最佳青少年表演獎<ref name="bbc wales">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/arts/sites/themes/film/christian_bale.shtml|title=Christian Bale|publisher=BBC Cymru Wales|access-date=2009-04-13|archive-date=2009-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090213150833/https://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/arts/sites/themes/film/christian_bale.shtml|url-status=live}}</ref>。成名讓貝爾在學校受到欺負，他也難以承受演員所帶來的壓力<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/2446065/Christian-Bale-profile.html|title=Christian Bale – profile|date=2008-07-22|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[每日電訊報|The Daily Telegraph]]|last=Singh|first=Anita|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180216081841/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/2446065/Christian-Bale-profile.html|archive-date=2018-02-16|url-status=live}}</ref>。在聚光燈下，他越來越懷疑是否該留在演藝界，但經濟原因讓他覺得自己有義務在年輕時繼續演戲<ref name="fame"/>。大約這個時候，演員兼導演[[簡尼夫·班納|簡尼夫·班納]]說服貝爾出演1989年電影《[[亨利五世_(1989年電影)|亨利五世]]》，讓他復出影壇<ref name="bbc wales"/>。隔年，貝爾在根據[[羅伯特·路易斯·史蒂文森|羅伯特·路易斯·史蒂文森]][[金銀島|同名小說]]改編的電視電影《{{tsl|en|Treasure Island (1990 film)|金银岛 (1990年电影)|-{zh-tw:金銀島爭霸戰; zh-cn:金银岛;}-}}》詮釋主角[[吉姆·霍金斯|吉姆·霍金斯]]，與[[查尔顿·赫斯顿|-{zh-hans:查尔顿·赫斯顿;zh-hk:查爾登·希士頓;zh-tw:卻爾登·希斯頓;}-]]飾演的[[約翰·西爾弗|約翰·西爾弗]]同台搭戲<ref>{{cite web|last1=Willman|first1=Chris|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-01-22-ca-417-story.html|title=TV Review : Hestons Sail for 'Treasure Island'|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|date=1990-01-22|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430110805/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-01-22-ca-417-story.html|archive-date=2021-04-30|url-status=live}}</ref>。

貝爾主演的1992年[[迪士尼|迪士尼]]歌舞片《{{tsl|en|Newsies|無冕天王|-{zh-cn:报童传奇;zh-hk:無冕天王;zh-tw:無冕天王;}-}}》票房失利，所獲評價也不佳<ref>{{cite web|last1=Jensen|first1=Jeff|url=https://ew.com/article/2012/07/17/the-dark-knight-rises-but-not-for-broadway-musicals-why-christian-bale-wont-be-seeing-newsies/|title=The Dark Knight Rises...but not for Broadway musicals: Why Christian Bale won't be seeing 'Newsies'|work=[[娛樂週刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2012-07-17|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126133057/https://ew.com/article/2012/07/17/the-dark-knight-rises-but-not-for-broadway-musicals-why-christian-bale-wont-be-seeing-newsies/|archive-date=2021-01-26|url-status=live}}</ref>。《[[紐約_(雜誌)|禿鷲]]》的麗貝卡·米爾佐夫（{{lang|en|Rebecca Milzoff}}）於2012年重看影片，她認為貝爾雖不是個好歌手，但演唱《聖達菲》（{{lang|en|"Santa Fe"}}）的嘶啞聲可愛又恰當<ref>{{cite web|last1=Milzoff|first1=Rebecca|url=https://www.vulture.com/2012/02/how-does-newsies-hold-up.html|title=How Does Newsies Hold Up?|website=[[紐約_(雜誌)|Vulture]]|date=2012-02-29|access-date=2021-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224183254/https://www.vulture.com/2012/02/how-does-newsies-hold-up.html|archive-date=2021-02-24|url-status=live}}</ref>。1993年，他出演《{{tsl|en|Swing Kids (1993 film)|搖擺狂潮}}》，講述[[納粹德國|納粹德國]]崛起時青少年偷聽被禁的[[爵士樂|爵士樂]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Maslin|first1=Janet|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1993/03/05/movies/review-film-jazz-in-nazi-germany-youthful-resistance.html|title=Review/Film; Jazz in Nazi Germany: Youthful Resistance|work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|date=1993-03-05|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308223440/https://www.nytimes.com/1993/03/05/movies/review-film-jazz-in-nazi-germany-youthful-resistance.html|archive-date=2021-03-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾經[[薇诺娜·瑞德|薇诺娜·瑞德]]推薦，在[[姬蓮·阿姆斯壯|姬蓮·阿姆斯壯]]1994年的電影《[[小婦人_(1994年電影)|-{zh-tw:新小婦人; zh-hk:小婦人; zh-hans:小妇人;}-]]》扮演[[小婦人|西奧多·「勞里」·勞倫斯]]<ref name="bbc wales"/>。電影無論商業還是評論都大獲成功<ref name="laurie">{{cite web|last1=Spencer|first1=Ashley|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/12/movies/little-women.html|title='Little Women': An Oral History of the 1994 Adaptation|work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|date=2019-09-12|access-date=2021-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208070613/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/12/movies/little-women.html|archive-date=2021-02-08|url-status=live}}</ref>，飾演女主角[[小婦人|喬·馬奇]]的-{zh-cn:瑞德; zh-tw:瑞德; zh-hk:維達;}-表示他捕捉到了角色的複雜本質<ref name="laurie"/>。他接著在1995年迪士尼動畫電影《[[风中奇缘_(电影)|风中奇缘]]》配音上尉[[約翰·史密斯_(探險家)|約翰·史密斯]]的年輕夥伴托馬斯（{{lang|en|Thomas}}），可惜評價差強人意<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cosmopolitan.com/entertainment/movies/g20634678/actors-disney-character-voices/|title=40 Actors You Completely Forgot Voiced Disney Characters|date=2020-08-20|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[柯夢波丹|Cosmopolitan]]|last1=Allen|first1=Kelly|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903022727/https://www.cosmopolitan.com/entertainment/movies/g20634678/actors-disney-character-voices/|archive-date=2020-09-03|url-status=live|last2=Miller|first2=Gregory E.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='Batman Forever' Bloodies 'Pocahontas'|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1995-06-30-9506300021-story.html|first1=John|last1=Horn|work=[[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]]|date=1995-06-30|access-date=2015-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150524095539/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1995-06-30/entertainment/9506300021_1_million-in-ticket-sales-studio-estimates-north-american-box-office|archive-date=2015-05-24|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾於在根據[[亨利·詹姆斯|亨利·詹姆斯]][[貴婦畫像|同名小說]]改編的1996年電影《[[妮可基嫚之風情萬種|-{zh-tw:妮可基嫚之風情萬種; zh-hk:淑女本色; zh-cn:淑女本色;}-]]》飾演小角色<ref name="every">{{Cite web|url=https://www.vulture.com/article/best-christian-bale-movies-ranked.html|title=The Best Christian Bale Movies, Ranked|date=2020-04-20|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[紐約_(雜誌)|Vulture]]|last1=Grierson|first1=Tim|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130192218/https://www.vulture.com/article/best-christian-bale-movies-ranked.html|archive-date=2021-01-30|url-status=live|last2=Leitch|first2=Will}}</ref>，並在1997年歌舞片《[[紫醉金迷|紫醉金迷]]》出演，影片背景設定在[[華麗搖滾|華麗搖滾]]風行的1970年代<ref name="masked">{{cite web|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2008/SHOWBIZ/Movies/07/28/christian.bale/index.html|title='Knight's' Bale: Who is that masked man?|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2008-07-28|access-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325035112/https://edition.cnn.com/2008/SHOWBIZ/Movies/07/28/christian.bale/index.html|archive-date=2021-03-25|url-status=live}}</ref>。1999年，貝爾在改編自[[威廉·莎士比亞|威廉·莎士比亞]][[仲夏夜之夢|同名劇作]]的[[群戲|群戲]]《{{tsl|en|A Midsummer Night's Dream (1999 film)|仲夏夜之夢 (1999年電影)|仲夏夜之夢}}》中與[[奇雲·格連|奇雲·格連]]和[[蜜雪兒·菲佛|蜜雪兒·菲佛]]合作，他在片中飾演{{tsl|en|Demetrius (A Midsummer Night's Dream)|狄米特律斯 (仲夏夜之夢)|狄米特律斯}}<ref>{{cite web|last1=Stack|first1=Peter|url=https://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Dream-Interpretation-Stellar-cast-adds-comic-2931131.php|title='Dream' Interpretation / Stellar cast adds comic madness to lush, over-the-top 'Midsummer'|work=[[舊金山紀事報|San Francisco Chronicle]]|date=1999-05-14|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024184040/https://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Dream-Interpretation-Stellar-cast-adds-comic-2931131.php|archive-date=2020-10-24|url-status=live}}</ref>。

===立足影壇但票房失利（2000至2004年）===
貝爾接下來主演改編自{{tsl|en|Bret Easton Ellis|佈雷特·伊斯頓·艾利斯}}[[美國殺人魔_(小說)|同名小說]]的《[[美色殺人狂|美色殺人狂]]》，該片講述股票投資人{{tsl|en|Patrick Bateman|派屈克·貝特曼}}私底下是連環殺手。導演{{tsl|en|Mary Harron|玛丽·哈伦|-{zh-cn:玛丽·哈伦; zh-tw:瑪麗·海隆;}-}}挑選貝爾出演時，遭到影片製片商兼發行公司[[獅門娛樂|獅門娛樂]]拒絕，並打算請[[奧利華·史東|奧利華·史東]]執導，而[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥]]飾演貝特曼，但兩人放棄作品後貝爾和-{zh-cn:哈伦; zh-tw:海隆;}-得以奪回原來位置<ref>{{cite web|last1=Gopalan|first1=Nisha|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2000/mar/24/fiction.breteastonellis|title=American Psycho: the story behind the film|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2000-03-23|access-date=2021-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225081010/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2000/mar/24/fiction.breteastonellis|archive-date=2021-02-25|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Mazziotta|first1=Julie|url=https://people.com/health/christian-bale-never-gone-to-gym-before-american-psycho/|title=Christian Bale 'Had Never Gone to a Gym' Before American Psycho|work=[[人物_(雜誌)|People]]|date=2020-01-22|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200123062634/https://people.com/health/christian-bale-never-gone-to-gym-before-american-psycho/|archive-date=2020-01-23|url-status=live}}</ref>。為了達到貝特曼輪廓分明的體形，貝爾花了數月鍛鍊和曬黑，並戴上牙套來揣摩角色自戀的性格<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fischer|first1=Paul|url=https://www.darkhorizons.com/christian-bale-for-american-psycho/|title=Unmasking an American Psycho|publisher=Dark Horizons|date=2000-04-14|access-date=2021-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202213854/http://www.darkhorizons.com/christian-bale-for-american-psycho/|archive-date=2018-02-02|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="teeth">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2000/apr/06/artsfeatures|title=The method in my madness|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2000-04-06|access-date=2021-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126185859/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2000/apr/06/artsfeatures|archive-date=2021-01-26|url-status=live}}</ref>。影片在2000年[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]舉行首映，[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]的安東尼·考夫曼（{{lang|en|Anthony Kaufman}}）評價它是盛事中最令人反感的電影<ref name="Kaufman">{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/people/int_Harron_Mary_000414.html|title=Interview: 9-Months Pregnant and Delivering "American Psycho," Director Mary Harron|date=2000-04-14|access-date=2021-04-30|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|last=Kaufman|first=Anthony|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081012093815/https://www.indiewire.com/people/int_Harron_Mary_000414.html|archive-date=2008-10-12|url-status=dead}}</ref>。影評人[[羅傑·埃伯特|羅傑·埃伯特]]對貝爾的演出表示「他讓角色從人見人愛跳到卑鄙無恥是非常花力氣的做法，完全沒有出於本能而放不開，這證明他是個好演員」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/american-psycho-2000|title=American Psycho|date=2000-04-14|access-date=2021-04-30|work=RogerEbert.com|last1=Ebert|first1=Roger|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120091611/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/american-psycho-2000|archive-date=2021-01-20|url-status=live|author-link=羅傑·埃伯特}}</ref>。影片於2000年4月上映，票房評價兩得意的它後來更成為[[邪典追捧|邪典追捧]]<ref name="psycho">{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/04/american-psycho-leo-dicaprio-patrick-bateman-1202224972/|title=Mary Harron Reflects on Nearly Losing 'American Psycho' Director Gig for Rejecting DiCaprio|date=2020-04-14|access-date=2021-04-30|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|last=Sharf|first=Zack|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311055807/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/04/american-psycho-leo-dicaprio-patrick-bateman-1202224972/|archive-date=2021-03-11|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Garner|first1=Dwight|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/27/theater/in-hindsight-an-american-psycho-looks-a-lot-like-us.html|title=In Hindsight, an 'American Psycho' Looks a Lot Like Us|work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|date=2016-03-24|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108175003/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/27/theater/in-hindsight-an-american-psycho-looks-a-lot-like-us.html|archive-date=2020-11-08|url-status=live}}</ref>，從此也奠定貝爾{{tsl|en|leading man|男主角}}的地位<ref name="first"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Desta|first1=Yohana|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/photos/2018/10/christian-bale-movie-transformations|title=Eight Times Christian Bale Totally Transformed for a Movie Role|work=[[名利场_(杂志)|Vanity Fair]]|date=2018-10-05|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112034929/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/photos/2018/10/christian-bale-movie-transformations|archive-date=2020-11-12|url-status=live}}</ref>。

《美色殺人狂》之後的四年裏，貝爾出演電影的票房和評價均以失敗收場<ref>{{cite web|last1=Dilard|first1=Clayton|url=https://www.slantmagazine.com/film/box-office-rap-out-of-the-furnace-and-christian-bales-body-of-work/|title=Box Office Rap: Out of the Furnace and Christian Bale's Body (of Work)|work=[[偏鋒雜誌|Slant Magazine]]|date=2013-12-03|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028175837/https://www.slantmagazine.com/film/box-office-rap-out-of-the-furnace-and-christian-bales-body-of-work/|archive-date=2020-10-28|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾在{{tsl|en|John Singleton|约翰·辛格顿}}的動作片《[[殺戮戰警|-{zh-tw:殺戮戰警;zh-hk:辣手刑警;zh-cn:杀戮战警;}-]]》飾演邪惡的房產繼承人<ref name="every"/>。他緊接著在根據{{tsl|en|Captain Corelli's Mandolin|柯雷利上尉的曼陀鈴|同名小說}}改編的《[[戰地情人|戰地情人]]》出演，該片由[[約翰·麥登|約翰·麥登]]執導，他飾演的希臘漁夫曼德拉斯（{{lang|en|Mandras}}）與柯雷利上尉（{{lang|en|Captain Corelli}}，[[尼古拉斯·凯奇|尼古拉斯·凯奇]]飾）爭奪愛人佩拉吉亞（{{lang|en|Pelagia}}，[[佩内洛普·克鲁兹|佩内洛普·克鲁兹]]飾）<ref name="every"/>。貝爾在出演《美色殺人狂》和《-{zh-tw:殺戮戰警;zh-hk:辣手刑警;zh-cn:杀戮战警;}-》後，他感覺飾演有人性情感的曼德拉斯十分耳目一新<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fuller|first1=Graham|url=https://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/new-again-christian-bale|title=New Again: Christian Bale|work=Interview|date=2012-07-17|access-date=2021-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122132305/https://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/new-again-christian-bale|archive-date=2021-01-22|url-status=live}}</ref>。2002年，他出演《{{tsl|en|Laurel Canyon (film)|桂冠街區|-{zh-tw:桂冠街區;zh-hk:桂冠街區;zh-cn:月桂谷;}-}}》、《[[火焰末日|火焰末日]]》和《[[撕裂的末日|-{zh-hk:未來殺人網絡; zh-tw:重裝任務; zh-cn:撕裂的末日;}-]]》三部電影<ref name="bbc wales"/>。《[[娛樂週刊|娛樂週刊]]》的{{tsl|en|Lisa Schwarzbaum|莉薩·施瓦茨鮑姆}}在評價《-{zh-tw:桂冠街區;zh-hk:桂冠街區;zh-cn:月桂谷;}-》時批評貝爾的演出「花裡胡哨」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Schwarzbaum|first1=Lisa|url=https://ew.com/article/2003/03/14/laurel-canyon-2/|title=Laurel Canyon|work=[[娛樂週刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2003-03-14|access-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029111628/https://ew.com/article/2003/03/14/laurel-canyon-2/|archive-date=2020-10-29|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾起初不太想加入有用[[電腦成像|電腦成像]]的[[末日幻想|後末日]]片《火焰末日》，但他後來表示自己很享受出演可能會失敗的電影，並透露導演{{tsl|en|Rob Bowman (filmmaker)|罗伯·鲍曼|-{zh-tw:羅布·鮑曼; zh-cn:罗伯·鲍曼;}-}}也是他決定參與的原因<ref>{{cite web|last1=Cawthorne|first1=Alec|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/arts/sites/christian-bale/pages/reign-of-fire.shtml|title=Christian Bale interview: Reign Of Fire (2002)|publisher=[[BBC威爾斯|BBC Cymru Wales]]|access-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227035724/https://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/arts/sites/christian-bale/pages/reign-of-fire.shtml|archive-date=2020-12-27|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Chavel">{{cite web|last1=Chavel|first1=Sean|url=http://www.ugo.com/channels/filmTv/features/reignoffire/christianbale.asp|title=Interview with Christian Bale of Reign of Fire|publisher=UGO Networks|access-date=2006-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050410033316/https://www.ugo.com/channels/filmTv/features/reignoffire/christianbale.asp|archive-date=2005-04-10|url-status=dead}}</ref>。另外，他在《-{zh-hk:未來殺人網絡; zh-tw:重裝任務; zh-cn:撕裂的末日;}-》飾演未來社會的警察，並表演融合槍戰的虛構武術[[槍械形|槍械形]]<ref name="every"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Francisco|first1=Eric|url=https://www.inverse.com/entertainment/movies-leaving-netflix-equilibrium|title=The one sci-fi movie you need to watch before it leaves Netflix this week|website=Inverse|date=2020-06-01|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122225053/https://www.inverse.com/entertainment/movies-leaving-netflix-equilibrium|archive-date=2021-01-22|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Lincoln|first1=Kevin|url=https://www.vulture.com/2016/10/john-wick-gun-fu.html|title=The Gun-Fu of John Wick and John Woo: A Primer|website=[[紐約_(雜誌)|Vulture]]|date=2016-10-12|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013130248/https://www.vulture.com/2016/10/john-wick-gun-fu.html|archive-date=2016-10-13|url-status=live}}</ref>。《[[IGN|IGN]]》的傑夫·奧托（{{lang|en|Jeff Otto}}）歸納《火焰末日》「不受待見」，《-{zh-hk:未來殺人網絡; zh-tw:重裝任務; zh-cn:撕裂的末日;}-》則「嚴重被低估」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Otto|first1=Jeff|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2005/06/14/interview-christian-bale-2|title=Interview: Christian Bale|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2005-06-15|access-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630223052/https://www.ign.com/articles/2005/06/14/interview-christian-bale-2|archive-date=2017-06-30|url-status=live}}</ref>。《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》的斯蒂芬·阿普爾鮑姆（{{lang|en|Stephen Applebaum}}）稱上述兩部電影、《-{zh-tw:殺戮戰警;zh-hk:辣手刑警;zh-cn:杀戮战警;}-》和《戰地情人》「平庸」<ref name="realistic">{{cite web|last1=Applebaum|first1=Stephen|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/christian-bale-cinema-s-extremist-484641.html|title=Christian Bale: Cinema's extremist|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|date=2005-02-25|access-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130180008/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/christian-bale-cinema-s-extremist-484641.html|archive-date=2021-01-30|url-status=live}}</ref>。

貝爾在心理驚悚片《[[克里斯汀貝爾之黑暗時刻|-{zh-hans:机械师; zh-hk:迷魂殺陣; zh-tw:克里斯汀貝爾之黑暗時刻;}-]]》主演被失眠折磨到心理失常的機械師。他最先準備角色時只靠吸煙和喝威士忌，後來他增餐至每天喝黑咖啡、吃一顆蘋果和一罐-{zh-cn:金枪鱼; zh-tw:鮪魚; zh-hk:吞拿魚;}-<ref>{{cite news|last1=Nash|first1=Brad|url=https://www.gq.com.au/entertainment/film-tv/the-story-of-christian-bales-the-machinist-transformation-is-insane/news-story/1892292672564838caf2106b38d9115d|title=The Story Of Christian Bale's The Machinist Transformation Is Insane|work=GQ Australia|date=2020-05-14|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118064043/https://www.gq.com.au/entertainment/film-tv/the-story-of-christian-bales-the-machinist-transformation-is-insane/news-story/1892292672564838caf2106b38d9115d|archive-date=2021-01-18|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Schwarzbaum|first1=Lisa|url=https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20140119-oscars-pounds-of-flesh|title=The Thin Men: Actors who starve themselves for an Oscar|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2014-01-21|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612072921/https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20140119-oscars-pounds-of-flesh|archive-date=2021-06-12|url-status=live}}</ref>。最後減了29公斤的貝爾以55公斤來扮演劇本中「骨瘦如柴」的角色<ref name="machinist">{{cite web|last1=Rosen|first1=Lisa|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2004-oct-21-wk-movies21-story.html|title=Losing himself in the role|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2004-10-21|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501055633/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2004-oct-21-wk-movies21-story.html|archive-date=2021-05-01|url-status=live}}</ref>，[[罗伯特·德尼罗|罗伯特·德尼罗]]在1980年電影《[[愤怒的公牛|愤怒的公牛]]》為角色{{tsl|en|Jake LaMotta|傑克·拉莫塔}}增重被拿來與其比較<ref>{{cite journal|last1=McClelland|first1=Nicholas Hegel|url=https://entertainment.time.com/2012/07/11/the-evolution-of-christian-bale/slide/the-machinist/|title=The Evolution of Christian Bale|journal=[[時代_(雜誌)|Time]]|date=2012-07-02|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191227122351/https://entertainment.time.com/2012/07/11/the-evolution-of-christian-bale/slide/the-machinist/|archive-date=2019-12-27|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾稱這段轉變讓他無比安逸，因為他一直待命等待能燃起興趣的劇本，正是這部影片讓他願意為角色減重<ref name="Movieweb">{{cite web|last=Topel|first=Fred|url=https://www.movieweb.com/news/NEHtLOKJ9zqXLO|title=Christian Bale talks The Machinist|date=2004-10-15|access-date=2008-05-05|publisher=MovieWeb|archive-date=2010-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100722015755/https://www.movieweb.com/news/NEHtLOKJ9zqXLO|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="stephenwales">{{cite web | title = Christian Bale interview: The Machinist (2004) | last = Applebaum | first = Stephen | publisher = BBC Cymru Wales | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/arts/sites/themes/film/christian_bale_machinist.shtml | access-date = 2009-04-20 | archive-date = 2020-12-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201227035450/https://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/arts/sites/christian-bale/pages/machinist.shtml | url-status = live }}</ref>。《-{zh-hans:机械师; zh-hk:迷魂殺陣; zh-tw:克里斯汀貝爾之黑暗時刻;}-》於2004年10月上映，但觀眾不買帳<ref name="machinist"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Lambie|first1=Ryan|url=https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/looking-back-at-the-machinist/|title=Looking back at The Machinist|publisher=Den of Geek|date=2012-08-08|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905092418/https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/looking-back-at-the-machinist/|archive-date=2020-09-05|url-status=live}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Orlando Sentinel|奧蘭多哨兵報}}》的羅傑·摩爾（{{lang|en|Roger Moore}}）將它評為年度最佳電影，《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的[[陶德·麥卡錫|陶德·麥卡錫]]稱讚貝爾「焦慮不安、咄咄逼人，最後無比痛苦的演技」給影片打了劑「強力定心針」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Moore|first1=Roger|url=https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-2004-12-10-0412090432-story.html|title=Bale Chills to the Bone|work=Orlando Sentinel|date=2004-12-10|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201155616/https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-2004-12-10-0412090432-story.html|archive-date=2020-12-01|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=McCarthy|first1=Todd|author-link1=陶德·麥卡錫|url=https://variety.com/2004/film/awards/the-machinist-1200536740/|title=The Machinist|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2004-01-29|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516003739/https://variety.com/2004/film/awards/the-machinist-1200536740/|archive-date=2021-05-16|url-status=live}}</ref>。

