貝爾在《[[蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻]]》主演化名為超級英雄[[蝙蝠俠|蝙蝠俠]]的美國億萬富翁[[蝙蝠俠|布魯斯·韋恩]]，是[[蝙蝠俠系列電影|蝙蝠俠系列電影]]的[[重啟_(虛構)|重啟片]]。導演[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]看到貝爾身上「完全處於黑暗與光明之間的平衡」，於是選擇當時還算名不見經傳的貝爾<ref name="greenberg20050508">{{Cite news |url=https://articles.latimes.com/2005/may/08/entertainment/ca-batman8 |title=Rescuing Batman |last=Greenberg |first=James |date=2005-05-08 |work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] |access-date=2019-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202014002/https://articles.latimes.com/2005/may/08/entertainment/ca-batman8 |archive-date=2008-12-02 |page=E-10 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3102536.stm|title=Actor Bale lands Batman role|publisher=[[BBC新聞|BBC News]]|date=2003-09-12|access-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081130111111/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3102536.stm|archive-date=2008-11-30|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾為角色增回《-{zh-hans:机械师; zh-hk:迷魂殺陣; zh-tw:克里斯汀貝爾之黑暗時刻;}-》失去的體重，並開始練肌肉，最後他重達100公斤<ref>{{cite web|last1=Dibin|first1=Emma|url=https://www.esquire.com/uk/culture/film/news/a9814/why-christian-bale-style-yo-yo-dieting-is-terrible-for-youy/|title=Why Christian Bale-Style Yo-Yo Dieting Is Terrible For You|work=[[君子雜誌|Esquire]]|date=2016-04-14|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112035108/https://www.esquire.com/uk/culture/film/news/a9814/why-christian-bale-style-yo-yo-dieting-is-terrible-for-youy/|archive-date=2020-11-12|url-status=live}}</ref>。他還練習武器、[[詠春拳|詠春]]和凱西格鬥術<ref>{{cite news|last1=Evans|first1=Matthew|url=https://www.menshealth.com/uk/fitness/a758307/5-of-christian-bales-craziest-body-transformations/|title=Christian Bale's 5 Craziest Body Transformations|work=[[男士健康|Men's Health]]|date=2017-02-11|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124050157/https://www.menshealth.com/uk/fitness/a758307/5-of-christian-bales-craziest-body-transformations/|archive-date=2021-01-24|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾得認可故事中的特殊情況，像是角色「覺得他能在半夜穿著蝙蝠裝跑來跑去」，並表示他和-{zh-cn:诺兰; zh-tw:諾蘭; zh-hk:路蘭;}-「儘量（故意貼近事情）真實動機」，例如韋恩父母遭到謀殺<ref name="realistic"/>。貝爾對韋恩和蝙蝠俠用了不同聲音，後者聲音比較沙啞，-{zh-cn:诺兰; zh-tw:諾蘭; zh-hk:路蘭;}-相信這能強化角色的視覺外貌<ref>{{cite web|last1=Maher|first1=John|url=https://www.polygon.com/2018/7/16/17574850/batman-dark-knight-christian-bale-voice|title=Christian Bale's infamous Dark Knight voice was the only option|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|date=2018-07-16|access-date=2021-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102173914/https://www.polygon.com/2018/7/16/17574850/batman-dark-knight-christian-bale-voice|archive-date=2021-01-02|url-status=live}}</ref>。2005年6月，《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|last1=Dargis|first1=Manohla|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2005/06/15/movies/dark-was-the-young-knight-battling-his-inner-demons.html|title=Dark Was the Young Knight Battling His Inner Demons|work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|date=2005-06-15|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529182857/https://www.nytimes.com/2005/06/15/movies/dark-was-the-young-knight-battling-his-inner-demons.html|archive-date=2015-05-29|url-status=live}}</ref>。《禿鷲》的蒂姆·格里森（{{lang|en|Tim Grierson}}）和{{tsl|en|Will Leitch|威爾·萊奇}}稱讚貝爾「敏感又聰明地詮釋出被寵壞、任性的布魯斯，（他）終於長大（並打擊犯罪）」<ref name="every"/>。貝爾因本片拿下[[MTV影視大獎最佳英雄|MTV影視大獎最佳英雄]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.smh.com.au/news/fashion/gay-cowboys-the-best-kissers/2006/06/04/1149359608529.html|title=Gay cowboys the best kissers|date=2006-06-04|work=[[雪梨晨鋒報|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|access-date=2009-04-13|archive-date=2009-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090606135909/https://www.smh.com.au/news/fashion/gay-cowboys-the-best-kissers/2006/06/04/1149359608529.html|url-status=live}}</ref>。

同年，貝爾在根據[[黛安娜·韋恩·瓊斯|黛安娜·韋恩·瓊斯]][[魔幻城堡|同名兒童小說]]改編的《[[霍爾的移動城堡|霍爾的移動城堡]]》英文版[[配音|配音]]名義巫師{{tsl|en|Wizard Howl|霍爾 (霍爾的移動城堡)|-{zh-cn:哈尔; zh-tw:霍爾; zh-hk:哈爾}-}}<ref>{{cite web|last1=Forbes|first1=Jake|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2005-jun-05-ca-howl5-story.html|title='Howl's' a natural draw for an anime master|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2005-06-05|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430151213/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2005-jun-05-ca-howl5-story.html|archive-date=2021-04-30|url-status=live}}</ref>，他後來承認是觀看導演[[宮崎駿|宮崎駿]]的動畫片《[[千与千寻|千与千寻]]》後才願意接下這差事<ref>{{cite web|last1=Winning|first1=Joshua|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/worst-to-best-christian-bale/4/|title=Worst To Best: Christian Bale|website=GamesRadar+|date=2012-08-07|access-date=2021-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210813104512/https://www.gamesradar.com/worst-to-best-christian-bale/4/|archive-date=2021-08-13|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾不久在[[大卫·阿耶|-{zh-cn:大卫·阿耶;zh-tw:大衛·艾亞;}-]]的犯罪片《{{tsl|en|Harsh Times|暴力衝擊|-{zh-cn:非常时期;zh-tw:暴力衝擊;}-}}》飾演患有[[創傷後壓力症候群|創傷後遺症]]的美國退伍軍人，該片在[[多倫多國際影展|多倫多國際影展]]舉行首映<ref name="every"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2005-07-26-blanchett-toronto_x.htm|title=Blanchett joins Toronto festival lineup|date=2005-07-26|work=[[今日美國|USA Today]]|access-date=2009-04-13|archive-date=2012-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120630224752/https://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2005-07-26-blanchett-toronto_x.htm|url-status=live}}</ref>。他接下來在[[歷史片|歷史片]]《[[新世界_(2005年电影)|新世界]]》詮釋定居者[[約翰·羅爾夫|約翰·羅爾夫]]，導演[[泰倫斯·馬利克|泰倫斯·馬利克]]根據[[寶嘉康蒂|寶嘉康蒂]]的故事創作劇情，影片於2005年12月25日上映<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/01/20/movies/a-briefer-account-of-jamestowns-founding.html|title=A Briefer Account of Jamestown's Founding|date=2006-01-20|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|last=Dargis|first=Manohla|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126214650/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/01/20/movies/a-briefer-account-of-jamestowns-founding.html|archive-date=2021-01-26|url-status=live}}</ref>。隔年，德國導演[[韋納·荷索|韋納·荷索]]推出新項目《[[重見天日|重見天日]]》，貝爾飾演在[[越戰|越戰]]出任務時遭到擊落後與死神搏鬥的美國[[戰鬥機|戰鬥機]]駕駛員{{tsl|en|Dieter Dengler|迪特爾·丹格拉}}<ref name="every"/>。兩人合作後，-{zh-cn:赫尔佐格;zh-hk:荷索;}-表示早在貝爾參演蝙蝠俠前，就覺得他是當代最偉大的天才<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.irishexaminer.com/lifestyle/arid-30250904.html|title=Herzog hails Bale|work=Irish Examiner|date=2006-03-24|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501074739/https://www.irishexaminer.com/lifestyle/arid-30250904.html|archive-date=2021-05-01|url-status=live}}</ref>。《[[奧斯汀紀事|奧斯汀紀事]]》的瑪喬麗·鮑姆加滕（{{lang|en|Marjorie Baumgarten}}）認為貝爾持續「熟練掌握另一種美國人格類型」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Baumgarten|first1=Marjorie|url=https://www.austinchronicle.com/events/film/2007-07-27/506339/|title=Rescue Dawn – Movie Review|work=[[奧斯汀紀事|The Austin Chronicle]]|date=2007-07-27|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303122623/https://www.austinchronicle.com/events/film/2007-07-27/506339/|archive-date=2021-03-03|url-status=live}}</ref>。

貝爾在2006年電影《[[頂尖對決|-{zh-hans:致命魔术; zh-tw:頂尖對決; zh-hk:死亡魔法;}-]]》與-{zh-cn:诺兰; zh-tw:諾蘭; zh-hk:路蘭;}-繼《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》後再度合作，導演表示貝爾是毛遂自薦加入劇組。這部改編自{{tsl|en|Christopher Priest (novelist)|克里斯多夫·普利斯特}}{{tsl|en|The Prestige|死亡魔術|同名小說}}的電影講述兩名[[維多利亞時代|維多利亞時代]]魔術師（貝爾和[[休·傑克曼|休·傑克曼]]）相互較勁<ref>{{cite web|last1=Jolin|first1=Dan|url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/the-prestige-inside-christopher-nolan-movie-magic-trick/|title=The Prestige: Inside Christopher Nolan's Movie Magic Trick|work=[[帝國雜誌|Empire]]|date=2020-08-17|access-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202120229/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/the-prestige-inside-christopher-nolan-movie-magic-trick/|archive-date=2021-02-02|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Carle|first1=Chris|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2006/10/12/casting-the-prestige|title=Casting The Prestige|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2006-10-12|access-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202045019/https://www.ign.com/articles/2006/10/12/casting-the-prestige|archive-date=2020-12-02|url-status=live}}</ref>。影片雖受到影評人認可，但票房表現卻相對平庸，4千萬美元預算最後只賺得1億1千萬美元<ref>{{cite web|last1=Child|first1=Ben|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/nov/28/prestige-novelist-christopher-nolans-batman-movies-boring-and-pretentious|title=Prestige novelist: Christopher Nolan's Batman movies 'boring and pretentious'|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2014-11-28|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000232/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/nov/28/prestige-novelist-christopher-nolans-batman-movies-boring-and-pretentious|archive-date=2020-11-12|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Sims|first1=David|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2020/08/inception-10-christopher-nolan-tenet/614920/|title='Inception' at 10: Christopher Nolan Is Still Saving Cinema|work=[[大西洋_(雜誌)|The Atlantic]]|date=2020-08-04|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227075244/https://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2020/08/inception-10-christopher-nolan-tenet/614920/|archive-date=2021-02-27|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Mendelson|first1=Scott|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2020/11/01/box-office-tenet-passes-chris-nolan-best-movie-but-after-we-collided-plunges-76/|title=Box Office: 'Tenet' Tops Chris Nolan's Best Movie, 'After We Collided' Plunges 76%|work=[[富比士|Forbes]]|date=2020-11-01|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612062032/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2020/11/01/box-office-tenet-passes-chris-nolan-best-movie-but-after-we-collided-plunges-76/|archive-date=2021-06-12|url-status=live}}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的{{tsl|en|A. O. Scott|A·O·史考特}}看出貝爾的「狂熱內質」，並覺得他的演技「值得細品」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Scott|first1=A. O.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/10/20/movies/20pres.html|title=Two Rival Magicians, and Each Wants the Other to Go Poof|work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|date=2006-10-20|access-date=2021-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126175548/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/10/20/movies/20pres.html|archive-date=2021-01-26|url-status=live}}</ref>。2007年，貝爾接著在劇情片《[[搖滾啟示錄|-{zh-cn:我不在那儿; zh-tw:搖滾啟示錄; zh-hk:七人一個卜戴倫;}-]]》飾演創作歌手[[鲍勃·迪伦|鲍勃·迪伦]]的兩個階段，並在《[[决斗犹马镇|决斗犹马镇]]》演繹尋求公義的牧牛人。他將自己詮釋的-{zh-cn:迪伦; zh-hk:戴倫; zh-tw:狄倫}-階段歸納成「兩個男人全力追求真理」，並表示參演《决斗犹马镇》是喜歡電影中能讓他「單純弄髒和在泥濘爬行」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nymag.com/guides/fallpreview/2007/movies/36619/|title=The Great Obsessive|date=2007-08-24|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[紐約_(雜誌)|New York]]|last=Hill|first=Logan|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410204925/https://nymag.com/guides/fallpreview/2007/movies/36619/|archive-date=2021-04-10|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=36600|title=3:10 to Yuma: Christian Bale vs. Russell Crowe|publisher=ComingSoon.net|date=2007-09-03|access-date=2010-02-26|archive-date=2009-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305051459/https://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=36600|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾在-{zh-cn:诺兰; zh-tw:諾蘭; zh-hk:路蘭;}-的《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》續集《[[黑暗騎士|黑暗騎士]]》重新演繹蝙蝠俠，影片於2008年7月在全球上映後評論界反應極佳，並成為第四部票房超過10億美金的電影<ref>{{cite web|last1=Stolworthy|first1=Jacob|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/the-dark-knight-joker-heath-ledger-netflix-b1816309.html|title=The Dark Knight almost featured a scene that would have changed the entire movie|website=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|date=2021-03-12|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312103148/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/the-dark-knight-joker-heath-ledger-netflix-b1816309.html|archive-date=2021-03-12|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Sharf|first1=Zack|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2018/07/christopher-nolan-the-dark-knight-imax-re-release-anniversary-1201985124/|title='The Dark Knight' Returning to IMAX Theaters|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|date=2018-07-18|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719111627/https://www.indiewire.com/2018/07/christopher-nolan-the-dark-knight-imax-re-release-anniversary-1201985124/|archive-date=2018-07-19|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾親自上陣表演特技，例如站在芝加哥[[威利斯大廈|威利斯大廈]]樓頂<ref>{{cite news|last1=Celizic|first1=Mike|url=https://www.today.com/popculture/christian-bale-ledger-had-wonderful-time-joker-wbna25673502|title=Christian Bale: Ledger had 'wonderful time' as Joker|work=Today|date=2008-07-14|access-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123224608/https://www.today.com/popculture/christian-bale-ledger-had-wonderful-time-joker-wbna25673502|archive-date=2020-11-23|url-status=live}}</ref>。許多影評人將《黑暗騎士》列為最佳[[超級英雄電影|超級英雄電影]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tapley|first1=Kristopher|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/in-contention/dark-knight-changed-movies-christopher-nolan-1202874041/|title='Dark Knight' Changed Movies, and the Oscars, Forever|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2018-07-17|access-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424223538/https://variety.com/2018/film/in-contention/dark-knight-changed-movies-christopher-nolan-1202874041/|archive-date=2021-04-24|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Dockterman|first1=Eliana|url=https://time.com/5353143/sequels-better-than-original/|title=35 Sequels That Are Better Than the Original Movie|work=[[時代_(雜誌)|Time]]|date=2018-08-30|access-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129193531/https://time.com/5353143/sequels-better-than-original/|archive-date=2021-01-29|url-status=live}}</ref>。

===《黑暗騎士》三部曲完結，並獲影評青睞（2009至2012年）===
2008年2月，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]宣布貝爾將在後末日動作片《[[魔鬼終結者：未來救贖|魔鬼終結者：未來救贖]]》主演反抗軍領袖[[約翰·康納|約翰·康納]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/film-terminator-dc-idUKN2628286120080227|title=New "Terminator" film set for May 2009 release|date=2008-02-06|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430090423/https://www.reuters.com/article/film-terminator-dc-idUKN2628286120080227|archive-date=2021-04-30|url-status=live|publisher=[[路透社|Reuters]]}}</ref>，導演[[喬瑟夫·麥克吉帝·尼克爾|麥克G]]稱讚貝爾是「當代最可靠的演員」<ref name="temper">{{cite web|last1=Anthony|first1=Andrew|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2009/may/17/profile-christian-bale-terminator-film|title=Christian Bale: The Terminator with a temper|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2009-05-16|access-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125213443/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2009/may/17/profile-christian-bale-terminator-film|archive-date=2021-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref>。2009年2月，貝爾在片場罵街的錄音遭到公開，內容是影片攝影指導{{tsl|en|Shane Hurlbut|肖恩·哈爾布特}}在拍攝貝爾和[[布莱斯·达拉斯·霍华德|-{zh-hk:拜絲·黛麗·侯活;zh-tw:布萊絲·達拉斯·霍華;zh-cn:布莱斯·达拉斯·霍华德;}-]]戲份時入鏡，此行徑讓他大飆髒話，最後貝爾威脅哈爾布特沒有被解僱他就退出<ref name="today">{{cite news|url=https://www.today.com/popculture/whoopi-goldberg-defends-christian-bale-wbna29001920|title=Whoopi Goldberg defends Christian Bale|access-date=2009-02-06|date=2009-02-03|work=[[今天_(NBC)|Today]]|archive-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180107041442/https://www.today.com/popculture/whoopi-goldberg-defends-christian-bale-wbna29001920|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="in_tirade">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/bale-turns-american-psycho-with-expletiveladen-tantrum-on-set-1544988.html|title=Bale turns American psycho with expletive-laden tantrum on set|access-date=2009-02-04|date=2009-02-04|last1=Adams|first1=Guy|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|archive-date=2009-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205081725/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/bale-turns-american-psycho-with-expletiveladen-tantrum-on-set-1544988.html|url-status=dead}}</ref>。影界幾位同僚為貝爾發聲，認為此事只是他對演戲的執著<ref name="today"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7871743.stm|title=Wrestler director supports Bale|access-date=2009-02-06|date=2009-02-05|publisher=[[BBC新聞|BBC News]]|archive-date=2009-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090216233828/https://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7871743.stm|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Romano|first1=Nick|url=https://ew.com/tv/sharon-stone-defends-christian-bale-over-famous-outburst-on-terminator-set/|title=Sharon Stone defends Christian Bale's famous Terminator outburst|work=[[娛樂週刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2021-03-25|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326135642/https://ew.com/tv/sharon-stone-defends-christian-bale-over-famous-outburst-on-terminator-set/|archive-date=2021-03-26|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾不久後公開道歉，自認這次爆發「不可原諒」，並表示他的行為「真的太超過」，最後聲稱自己已向哈爾布特作出補償<ref name="kroq">{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/06/bale.apology/index.html|title=Bale apologizes for 'Terminator' tantrum|last=Duke|first=Alan|date=2009-02-06|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|access-date=2009-04-13|archive-date=2020-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128232914/https://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/06/bale.apology/index.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="bbcnews20090206">{{cite news|title=Actor Bale speaks out over rant|publisher=[[BBC新聞|BBC News]]|date=2009-02-06|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7875756.stm|access-date=2009-02-06|archive-date=2019-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021040758/https://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7875756.stm|url-status=live}}</ref>。《魔鬼終結者：未來救贖》於2009年5月上映，反應十分平淡<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/21/movies/21term.html|title=A Crude, Imperfect Enemy, Bolts and All, in McG's Film|date=2009-05-20|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|last=Scott|first=A. O.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308232601/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/21/movies/21term.html|archive-date=2021-03-08|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="salvation">{{cite web|last1=Child|first1=Ben|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/dec/03/christian-bale-i-wont-be-back-to-work-with-mcg|title=Christian Bale: I won't be back to work with McG|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2014-12-03|access-date=2021-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130115200/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/dec/03/christian-bale-i-wont-be-back-to-work-with-mcg|archive-date=2021-01-30|url-status=live}}</ref>。《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的{{tsl|en|Claudia Puig|克勞蒂亞·普格}}批評貝爾的演技「出奇地單一」，而《[[世紀報|世紀報]]》的傑克·威爾遜（{{lang|en|Jake Wilson}}）更認為這是他最沒說服力的演出<ref>{{cite web|last1=Puig|first1=Claudia|url=https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2009-05-19-terminator-salvation_N.htm|title=There's little to salvage from this 'Terminator'|work=[[今日美國|USA Today]]|date=2009-05-20|access-date=2021-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015173849/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2009-05-19-terminator-salvation_N.htm|archive-date=2020-10-15|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Wilson|first1=Jake|url=https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2009-05-19-terminator-salvation_N.htm|title=Headed for termination not salvation|work=[[世紀報|The Age]]|date=2009-06-04|access-date=2021-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191104033203/https://www.theage.com.au/entertainment/movies/headed-for-termination-not-salvation-20090604-ge7wqj.html|archive-date=2019-11-04|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾後來承認自己在製作期間就知道影片不會如他所願振興[[终结者电影系列|《终结者》電影系列]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sharf|first1=Zack|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2018/01/christian-bale-terminator-salvation-turned-down-role-statement-1201915441/|title=Christian Bale Never Wanted to Star in 'Terminator Salvation' and Said No Three Times: 'It's a Great Thorn in My Side'|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|date=2018-01-09|access-date=2021-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228033933/https://www.indiewire.com/2018/01/christian-bale-terminator-salvation-turned-down-role-statement-1201915441/|archive-date=2021-02-28|url-status=live}}</ref>，更斷言不會再與麥克G合作<ref name="salvation"/>。

