貝爾在[[麥可·曼恩|麥可·曼恩]]的犯罪劇情片《[[頭號公敵|頭號公敵]]》出演聯邦調查局探員{{tsl|en|Melvin Purvis|梅爾文·珀維斯}}，與飾演[[約翰·迪林傑|約翰·迪林傑]]的[[強尼·戴普|強尼·戴普]]同台搭戲<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204621904574248243614110928|title=Christian Bale and Michael Mann on John Dillinger, Gangsters, and 'Public Enemies'|date=2009-07-16|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[華爾街日報|The Wall Street Journal]]|last=Jurgensen|first=John|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430080505/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204621904574248243614110928|archive-date=2021-04-30|url-status=live}}</ref>。影片於2009年7月上映後名利雙收<ref>{{cite web|last1=Donahue|first1=Ann|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-goldenthal-idUSTRE56H08V20090718|title=Q&A: "Enemies" composer gives voice to "inner snarling"|publisher=[[路透社|Reuters]]|date=2009-07-18|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518052858/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-goldenthal-idUSTRE56H08V20090718|archive-date=2021-05-18|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Stolworthy|first1=Jacob|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/michael-mann-public-enemies-johnny-depp-john-dillinger-christian-bale-a7205411.html|title=Michael Mann toned down Public Enemies scene because the real-life events were so unbelievable|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|date=2016-08-23|access-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605154209/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/michael-mann-public-enemies-johnny-depp-john-dillinger-christian-bale-a7205411.html|archive-date=2021-06-05|url-status=live}}</ref>。《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的丹·扎克（{{lang|en|Dan Zak}}）不喜歡貝爾和-{zh-cn:德普;zh-hk:特普;zh-tw:戴普;zh-sg:特普;}-的選角，認為他們所飾角色的敵對性缺乏刺激，而《[[新共和|新共和]]》的克里斯托弗·奧爾（{{lang|en|Christopher Orr}}）稱讚貝爾「典型內向」演技「依舊有效」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Zak|first1=Dan|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/06/30/AR2009063004267.html|title=Movie Review: 'Public Enemies' With Johnny Depp|work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]]|date=2009-07-01|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924170536/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/06/30/AR2009063004267.html|archive-date=2020-09-24|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|last1=Orr|first1=Christopher|url=https://newrepublic.com/article/62989/the-movie-review-public-enemies|title=The Movie Review: 'Public Enemies'|magazine=[[新共和|The New Republic]]|date=2009-07-02|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227125952/https://newrepublic.com/article/62989/the-movie-review-public-enemies|archive-date=2021-02-27|url-status=live}}</ref>。隔年，貝爾在[[大卫·欧·拉塞尔|-{zh-hans:大卫·欧·拉塞尔;zh-hk:大衛·奧·羅素;zh-tw:大衛·歐·羅素;}-]]的劇情片《[[燃燒鬥魂|-{zh-hans:斗士; zh-tw:燃燒鬥魂; zh-hk:擊情手足;}-]]》出演染上毒癮自毀前程的專業拳擊手{{tsl|en|Dicky Eklund|狄奇·艾克倫德}}，並圍繞他和拳擊練習生弟弟{{tsl|en|Micky Ward|米奇·華德}}（[[馬克·華伯格|馬克·華伯格]]飾）的關係。貝爾在角色塑造注入幽默感來平衡艾克倫德的悲慘遭遇，更為此減了14公斤，《[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]]》的{{tsl|en|Mick LaSalle|米克·拉塞爾}}稱讚這為「精明觀察出確切身材和敏銳心理」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Riley|first1=Jenelle|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-contender-idUSTRE6AO0SQ20101125|title=The great "Contender" – Christian Bale cracks wise|publisher=[[路透社|Reuters]]|date=2010-11-25|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501082254/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-contender-idUSTRE6AO0SQ20101125|archive-date=2021-05-01|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=LaSalle|first1=Mick|url=https://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/The-Fighter-review-Actors-pack-a-punch-2453035.php|title='The Fighter' review: Actors pack a punch|work=[[舊金山紀事報|San Francisco Chronicle]]|date=2010-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926040813/https://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/The-Fighter-review-Actors-pack-a-punch-2453035.php|archive-date=2020-09-26|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾憑此片奪得[[奧斯卡最佳男配角獎|奧斯卡最佳男配角獎]]和[[金球獎最佳電影男配角|金球獎最佳電影男配角]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Christian Bale wins Oscar for "The Fighter"|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-oscars-supportactor-idUSTRE71R0OX20110228|access-date=2021-07-13|publisher=[[路透社|Reuters]]|date=2011-02-28|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807020324/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-oscars-supportactor-idUSTRE71R0OX20110228|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="screendaily">{{cite news|last1=Kay|first1=Jeremy|url=https://www.screendaily.com/news/christian-bale-thanks-satan-in-golden-globes-speech/5135578.article|title=Christian Bale thanks 'Satan' in Golden Globes speech|work=Screen Daily|date=2019-01-07|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108230537/https://www.screendaily.com/news/christian-bale-thanks-satan-in-golden-globes-speech/5135578.article|archive-date=2020-11-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。2011年，他參演[[張藝謀|張藝謀]]的歷史劇情片《[[金陵十三釵|金陵十三釵]]》，該片是當年最高票房的中國電影<ref name="highest">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-16638897|title=The story behind Chinese war epic The Flowers of War|publisher=[[BBC新聞|BBC News]]|date=2012-01-24|access-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212230328/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-16638897|archive-date=2018-01-12|url-status=live}}</ref>，影評界批判它「民族主義」、「反日」和「太長、太矯情和太膚淺」<ref name="highest"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=von Tunzelmann|first1=Alex|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2012/aug/02/flowers-of-war-chinese-film|title=The Flowers of War fails to bloom for Chinese film industry|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2012-08-02|access-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123122301/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2012/aug/02/flowers-of-war-chinese-film|archive-date=2018-11-23|url-status=live}}</ref>。

貝爾在克里斯多福·諾蘭執導的續集《[[黑暗騎士：黎明昇起|黑暗騎士：黎明昇起]]》三度演繹蝙蝠俠，影片於2012年7月上映<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mitchell|first1=Robert|url=https://variety.com/2012/film/news/biz-nation-reel-from-colorado-shooting-1118056834/|title=Biz, nation reel from Colorado shooting|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2012-07-20|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160923161837/https://variety.com/2012/film/news/biz-nation-reel-from-colorado-shooting-1118056834/|archive-date=2016-09-23|url-status=live}}</ref>。他稱電影中的蝙蝠俠飽受病魔和心理障礙折磨，並在《黑暗騎士》事件後一蹶不振<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hiscock|first1=John|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/9396277/Christian-Bale-interview-The-Dark-Knight-Rises.html|title=Christian Bale interview: The Dark Knight Rises|work=The Daily Telegraph、|date=2012-07-18|access-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427043750/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/9396277/Christian-Bale-interview-The-Dark-Knight-Rises.html|archive-date=2020-04-27|url-status=live}}</ref>。在美國[[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]][[奧羅拉_(科羅拉多州)|奧羅拉]]的電影午夜場發生[[2012年奧羅拉槍擊事件|槍擊案]]後，貝爾和妻子探望倖存者、醫生和{{tsl|en|The Medical Center of Aurora|奧羅拉醫療中心}}現場應急人員，並向受害者表示哀悼<ref name="Denver Post">{{cite web|last1=Lee|first1=Kurtis|last2=Parker|first2=Ryan|url=https://www.denverpost.com/breakingnews/ci_21147699/christian-bale-town-visiting-victims-shooting/|title=Batman actor Christian Bale visits victims, hospital personnel|work=[[丹佛郵報|The Denver Post]]|access-date=2012-07-26|date=2012-07-24|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091932/https://www.denverpost.com/breakingnews/ci_21147699/christian-bale-town-visiting-victims-shooting/|url-status=live}}</ref>。《黑暗騎士：黎明昇起》是第11部全球票房超過10億的電影，收益甚至超越《黑暗騎士》<ref>{{cite web|last1=Finke|first1=Nikki|url=https://deadline.com/2012/09/the-dark-knight-rises-becomes-11th-film-in-history-to-pass-1b-milestone-328349/|title='The Dark Knight Rises' Becomes 11th Film in History To Pass $1 Billion Milestone|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2012-09-03|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125213907/https://deadline.com/2012/09/the-dark-knight-rises-becomes-11th-film-in-history-to-pass-1b-milestone-328349/|archive-date=2021-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref>，造就諾蘭的[[黑暗騎士三部曲|《黑暗騎士》三部曲]]成為最賣座系列電影<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ryan|first1=Joal|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/pictures/biggest-movie-franchises-marvel-star-wars-harry-potter-and-more-ranked-by-box-office/|title=Biggest movie franchises: Marvel, Star Wars, Harry Potter and more ranked by box office|publisher=[[CBS新聞|CBS News]]|date=2020-01-24|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612050647/https://www.cbsnews.com/pictures/biggest-movie-franchises-marvel-star-wars-harry-potter-and-more-ranked-by-box-office/|archive-date=2021-06-12|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Eames|first1=Tom|url=https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/g24620/highest-grossing-franchises/?slide=31|title=The highest-grossing film franchises – the 50 biggest film series ever|publisher=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|date=2017-08-23|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612052617/https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/g24620/highest-grossing-franchises/?slide=31|archive-date=2021-06-12|url-status=live}}</ref>，也被評論界認為是最佳漫畫改編系列電影<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sharf|first1=Zack|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/11/christian-bale-turned-down-fourth-batman-movie-christopher-nolan-1202190295/|title=Christian Bale Turned Down Request for Fourth Batman Movie Because of Nolan's Wish|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|date=2019-11-18|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127180928/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/11/christian-bale-turned-down-fourth-batman-movie-christopher-nolan-1202190295/|archive-date=2020-11-27|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾在三部電影的演技廣受好評<ref name="first"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://apnews.com/article/6aae504d5b024655bf6cd6bd859a6ead|title=Christian Bale keen for Star Wars role|date=2018-01-05|access-date=2021-04-30|publisher=[[美聯社|Associated Press]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430025955/https://apnews.com/article/6aae504d5b024655bf6cd6bd859a6ead|archive-date=2021-04-30|url-status=live}}</ref>，《[[衛報|衛報]]》、《[[新音樂快遞|新音樂快遞]]》和《[[廣播時報|廣播時報]]》的調查評他是電影中蝙蝠俠的最佳詮釋<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bradshaw|first1=Paul|url=https://www.nme.com/features/batman-ranked-2901857|title=Every actor who's played Batman – ranked from worst to best|work=[[新音樂快遞|NME]]|date=2021-03-17|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317091220/https://www.nme.com/features/batman-ranked-2901857|archive-date=2021-03-17|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Child|first1=Ben|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/mar/04/why-christian-bale-will-always-be-the-best-batman|title=Why Christian Bale will always be the best Batman|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2016-03-04|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205185638/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/mar/04/why-christian-bale-will-always-be-the-best-batman|archive-date=2021-02-05|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.radiotimes.com/tv/sci-fi/christian-bale-best-batman/|title=Christian Bale voted the best Batman ever by fans|work=[[廣播時報|Radio Times]]|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501100814/https://www.radiotimes.com/tv/sci-fi/christian-bale-best-batman/|archive-date=2021-05-01|url-status=live}}</ref>。他後來透露不太滿意自己在三部曲的表現，表示他「沒太演好」自己的戲份，以及「沒太做到」他心中自己演蝙蝠俠應有的樣子<ref>{{cite web|last1=Stolworthy|first1=Jacob|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/christian-bale-doesn-t-rate-his-batman-performance-in-the-dark-knight-trilogy-a6911051.html|title=Christian Bale doesn't rate his Batman performance in the Dark Knight trilogy|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|date=2016-03-04|access-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420192637/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/christian-bale-doesn-t-rate-his-batman-performance-in-the-dark-knight-trilogy-a6911051.html|archive-date=2021-04-20|url-status=live}}</ref>。

===持續奪得好評（2013至2018年）===
2013年，貝爾在[[史考特·庫柏|-{zh-hk:史葛·古巴;zh-tw:史考特·庫柏;zh-cn:斯科特·库珀;}-]]的驚悚片《[[逃出鎔爐|逃出鎔爐]]》出演鋼鐵廠工人<ref>{{cite web|last1=Dargis|first1=Manohla|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/04/movies/out-of-the-furnace-with-christian-bale.html|title='Out of the Furnace,' With Christian Bale|work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|date=2013-12-03|access-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211201007/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/04/movies/out-of-the-furnace-with-christian-bale.html|archive-date=2020-12-11|url-status=live}}</ref>。-{zh-hk:古巴;zh-tw:庫柏;zh-cn:库珀;}-與貝爾見面前就為他重新打磨劇本，而且要他參演才會持續製作項目<ref name="plays"/>。影評人稱讚該片，並認為它是貝爾步入蝙蝠俠下一階段的首戰告捷<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lang|first1=Brent|url=https://www.thewrap.com/furnace-reviews-critics-think-another-deer-hunter/|title='Out of the Furnace' Reviews: Do Critics Think It's Another 'Deer Hunter'?|work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]|date=2013-11-11|access-date=2021-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823043203/https://www.thewrap.com/furnace-reviews-critics-think-another-deer-hunter/|archive-date=2014-08-23|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Labrecque|first1=Jeff|url=https://ew.com/article/2013/12/06/christian-bale-out-of-the-furnace-reviews/|title='Out of the Furnace': The reviews are in...|work=[[娛樂週刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-12-06|access-date=2021-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122065954/https://ew.com/article/2013/12/06/christian-bale-out-of-the-furnace-reviews/|archive-date=2021-01-22|url-status=live}}</ref>，《綜藝》的克里絲托弗·塔普利（{{lang|en|Kristopher Tapley}}）更覺得這是貝爾最好的電影演出<ref name="variety">{{cite web|last1=Tapley|first1=Kristopher|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/in-contention/top-10-christian-bale-performances-1202540158/|title=Top 10 Christian Bale Performances|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2017-08-31|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222061439/https://variety.com/2017/film/in-contention/top-10-christian-bale-performances-1202540158/|archive-date=2021-02-22|url-status=live}}</ref>。同年的《[[美国骗局|美国骗局]]》是貝爾和-{zh-hans:大卫·欧·拉塞尔;zh-hk:大衛·奧·羅素;zh-tw:大衛·歐·羅素;}-繼《-{zh-hans:斗士; zh-tw:燃燒鬥魂; zh-hk:擊情手足;}-》第二次合作<ref name="David O. Russell Project">{{cite web|last1=Reid|first1=Joe|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2013/12/american-hustle-fact-sheet/356041/|title='American Hustle' Can't Close the Deal|work=[[大西洋_(雜誌)|The Atlantic]]|date=2013-12-13|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118020815/https://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2013/12/american-hustle-fact-sheet/356041/|archive-date=2021-01-18|url-status=live}}</ref>。為飾演騙子厄文·羅森菲（{{lang|en|Irving Rosenfeld}}），貝爾學習現實生活的騙子{{tsl|en|Mel Weinberg|梅爾·溫伯格}}的採訪片段來充當靈感<ref name="plays"/>，更增重20公斤、剃頭和常用懶人姿勢，後者舉動讓他矮了7.6厘米，更讓他患得[[椎間盤脫出症|椎間盤突出]]<ref name="vicetransformation">{{Cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/la-en-mn-christian-bale-vice-20190129-story.html|title=Christian Bale: Man of a thousand physiques|date=2019-01-29|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|last=Hart|first=Hugh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121125733/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/la-en-mn-christian-bale-vice-20190129-story.html|archive-date=2021-01-21|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Christian Bale's 'American Hustle' Transformation Even Fooled Co-Star|author=Rosen, Christopher|date=2013-12-20|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/christian-bale-american-hustle_n_4412611|work=[[哈芬登郵報|HuffPost]]|access-date=2014-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120141926/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/christian-bale-american-hustle_n_4412611|archive-date=2021-01-20|url-status=live}}</ref>。-{zh-hans:拉塞尔;zh-hk:羅素;zh-tw:羅素;}-表示飾演無名角色的罗伯特·德尼罗在演員首次登場時沒有認出貝爾<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bernstein|first1=Paula|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2013/12/10-new-things-we-learned-about-american-hustle-de-niro-didnt-recognize-christian-bale-why-bradley-cooper-curled-his-hair-more-241428/|title=10 New Things We Learned About 'American Hustle:' De Niro Didn't Recognize Christian Bale, Why Bradley Cooper Curled His Hair & More|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|date=2013-12-11|access-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118045637/https://www.indiewire.com/2013/12/10-new-things-we-learned-about-american-hustle-de-niro-didnt-recognize-christian-bale-why-bradley-cooper-curled-his-hair-more-241428/|archive-date=2021-01-18|url-status=live}}</ref>。《[[紐約每日新聞|紐約每日新聞]]》的喬·紐邁爾（{{lang|en|Joe Neumaier}}）稱讚貝爾的演出「悲傷、有趣又引人入勝」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Neumaier|first1=Joe|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/american-hustle-movie-review-article-1.1545755|title='American Hustle': Movie review|work=[[紐約每日新聞|New York Daily News]]|date=2013-12-12|access-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217163111/https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/american-hustle-movie-review-article-1.1545755|archive-date=2020-12-17|url-status=live}}</ref>。此片為他贏得[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]和[[金球獎|金球獎]]提名<ref name="screendaily"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Merry|first1=Stephanie|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2014/02/27/why-american-hustle-should-win-the-best-picture-oscar/|title=Why 'American Hustle' should win the Best Picture Oscar|work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]]|date=2014-02-27|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118014956/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2014/02/27/why-american-hustle-should-win-the-best-picture-oscar/|archive-date=2021-01-18|url-status=live}}</ref>。

貝爾在[[雷利·史考特|雷利·史考特]]的史詩片《[[出埃及記：天地王者|出埃及記：天地王者]]》詮釋[[摩西|摩西]]。影片於2014年12月上映，但後來被指控白人演員扮演[[中東|中東]]角色，-{zh-hans:斯科特; zh-tw:史考特; zh-hk:史葛;}-為此澄清因為要融資才將角色[[電影的洗白|洗白]]，貝爾更力挺-{zh-hans:斯科特; zh-tw:史考特; zh-hk:史葛;}-製作電影時已坦誠相待<ref>{{cite web|last1=Child|first1=Ben|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/dec/09/christian-bale-defends-ridley-scott-exodus-whitewashing|title=Christian Bale defends Ridley Scott over Exodus 'whitewashing'|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2014-12-09|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227045851/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/dec/09/christian-bale-defends-ridley-scott-exodus-whitewashing|archive-date=2021-02-27|url-status=live}}</ref>。電影評價褒貶不一<ref>{{cite news|last1=Faughdner|first1=Ryan|title='Exodus: Gods and Kings' rides in with $1.2 million Thursday night|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-exodus-gods-kings-thursday-night-20141212-story.html|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2014-12-12|access-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731025001/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-exodus-gods-kings-thursday-night-20141212-story.html|archive-date=2020-07-31|url-status=live}}</ref>，《{{tsl|en|St. Louis Post-Dispatch|聖路易斯郵報}}》的喬·威廉姆斯（{{lang|en|Joe Williams}}）稱這是貝爾職業生涯中最吊兒郎當的演技<ref>{{cite web|last1=Williams|first1=Joe|url=http://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/movies/reviews/thou-shalt-not-waste-time-on-this-movie/article_fea4311d-cfa4-56f1-b31e-4b5390c5ed8c.html|title=Thou shalt not waste time on 'Exodus: Gods and Kings'|work=St. Louis Post-Dispatch|date=2014-12-11|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201143426/http://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/movies/reviews/thou-shalt-not-waste-time-on-this-movie/article_fea4311d-cfa4-56f1-b31e-4b5390c5ed8c.html|archive-date=2017-12-01|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾參演泰倫斯·馬利克的劇情片《[[聖杯騎士|聖杯騎士]]》，《[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋]]》影評人大衛·西姆斯（{{lang|en|David Sims}}）感嘆它「就算預料失敗還是要嘗試」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sims|first1=David|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/03/knight-of-cups-malick-review/472050/|title=Movie Review: 'Knight of Cups,' with Christian Bale, Cate Blanchett, and Natalie Portman, Is Terrence Malick's Version of Hollywood Satire|work=The Atlantic|date=2016-03-03|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026013241/https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/03/knight-of-cups-malick-review/472050/|archive-date=2020-10-26|url-status=live}}</ref>。他在[[第65屆柏林影展|第65屆柏林影展]]首映式上表示作品拍攝時完全沒有對白，馬利克只提供人物小傳給他<ref>{{cite web|last1=Child|first1=Ben|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/feb/09/christian-bale-terrence-malick-knight-of-cups|title=Christian Bale baffled by Terrence Malick on Knight of Cups shoot|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2021-02-09|access-date=2021-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202202831/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/feb/09/christian-bale-terrence-malick-knight-of-cups|archive-date=2020-12-02|url-status=live}}</ref>。不久後，他在關於[[2007年－2008年環球金融危機|2007年－2008年環球金融危機]]的傳記式喜劇劇情片《[[大賣空_(電影)|大賣空]]》飾演反社會避險基金經理[[麥可·貝瑞|麥可·貝瑞]]，該片由[[亞當·麥凱|亞當·麥凱]]執導<ref name="every"/>。他為電影配戴[[義眼|義眼]]<ref>{{cite web | url=https://variety.com/2015/film/reviews/the-big-short-review-1201639770/ | title=Film Review: 'The Big Short' | work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | date=2015-11-13 | access-date=2016-01-27 | last1=Barker |first1=Andrew | archive-date=2016-01-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129223612/https://variety.com/2015/film/reviews/the-big-short-review-1201639770/ | url-status=live }}</ref>，《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》的{{tsl|en|Joe Morgenstern|喬·摩根斯坦}}認為他的詮釋「好笑到令人害怕，或者（可能）是巧妙地剪出俏皮話和快照」<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-big-short-review-the-comic-beauties-of-a-bubble-1449771708|title='The Big Short' Review: The Comic Beauties of a Bubble|work=[[華爾街日報|The Wall Street Journal]]|date=2015-12-10|access-date=2016-01-27|last1=Morgenstern|first1=Joe|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127020051/https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-big-short-review-the-comic-beauties-of-a-bubble-1449771708|url-status=live}}</ref>，此角讓貝爾入圍奧斯卡金像獎和金球獎最佳男配角<ref>{{cite web|last1=King|first1=Susan|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-big-short-wins-oscar-adapted-screenplay-20160225-story.html|title='The Big Short' wins the Oscar for adapted screenplay|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2016-02-28|access-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701150452/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-big-short-wins-oscar-adapted-screenplay-20160225-story.html|archive-date=2017-07-01|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Lang|first1=Brent|title='Carol,' Netflix Lead Golden Globes Nomination|url=https://variety.com/2015/film/awards/golden-globe-nominations-2016-1201658153/|access-date=2016-01-27|work=Variety|date=2015-12-10|archive-date=2015-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211033745/https://variety.com/2015/film/awards/golden-globe-nominations-2016-1201658153/|url-status=live}}</ref>。

