-09|url-status=live}}</ref>，貝爾演這部戲時更學到[[夏延語|夏延語]]<ref name="Cheyenne"/>。《[[帝國_(雜誌)|帝國]]》影評人丹·喬林（{{lang|en|Dan Jolin}}）稱讚他的演技引人注目，並且是他演藝生涯中最突出的表演<ref>{{cite web|last1=Jolin|first1=Dan|url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/hostiles-review/|title=Hostiles Review|work=Empire|date=2017-09-04|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217182154/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/hostiles-review/|archive-date=2019-12-17|url-status=live}}</ref>。2018年，貝爾在冒險片《[[森林之子毛克利|森林之子毛克利]]》配音{{link-en|巴希拉|Bagheera}}，《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》的大衛·費婭爾（{{lang|en|David Fear}}）評價他和導演[[安迪·瑟克斯|安迪·瑟克斯]]的成功配音「帶出靈魂、喧哗和骚动」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fear|first1=David|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-reviews/mowgli-movie-review-761718/|title='Mowgli' Review: Welcome to the Jungle (Book)|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]]|date=2018-12-02|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181204131600/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-reviews/mowgli-movie-review-761718/|archive-date=2018-12-04|url-status=live}}</ref>。

