itics on Dick Cheney Film Starring Christian Bale|website=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2018-12-17|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518040928/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/vice-reviews-critics-dick-cheney-film-starring-christian-bale-1170063/|archive-date=2021-05-18|url-status=live}}</ref>，該角更讓他奪得[[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影男主角|金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影男主角]]，並入圍奧斯卡金像獎<ref name="WaPoVice">{{cite web|last1=Phillips|first1=Kristine|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/arts-entertainment/2019/01/07/christian-bale-thanked-satan-his-portrayal-dick-cheney-church-satan-approves/|title=Christian Bale thanked Satan for his portrayal of Dick Cheney. The Church of Satan approves.|work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]]|date=2019-01-08|access-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110081055/https://www.washingtonpost.com/arts-entertainment/2019/01/07/christian-bale-thanked-satan-his-portrayal-dick-cheney-church-satan-approves/|archive-date=2020-11-10|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/426369-christian-bale-gets-oscar-nomination-for-cheney-portrayal|title=Christian Bale gets Oscar nomination for Cheney portrayal|date=2019-01-22|access-date=2021-04-30|website=The Hill|last=Kurtz|first=Judy|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630153943/https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/426369-christian-bale-gets-oscar-nomination-for-cheney-portrayal|archive-date=2019-06-30|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾在[[第76屆金球獎|第76屆金球獎]]講獲獎感言時，有感謝[[撒旦|撒旦]]作為飾演-{zh-hans:切尼;zh-hk:切尼;zh-tw:錢尼;}-的靈感，此番言論引起-{zh-hans:切尼;zh-hk:切尼;zh-tw:錢尼;}-女兒、[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院成員]][[利茲·切尼|-{zh:利茲·切尼;zh-hans:利茲·切尼;zh-hk:利茲·切尼;zh-tw:麗茲·錢尼;}-]]反彈，表示貝爾糟蹋飾演「真實英雄」的機會<ref>{{cite web|last1=Samuels|first1=Brett|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/house/424492-liz-cheney-responds-to-christian-bale-calling-father-satan-he-had-the-chance|title=Liz Cheney on Christian Bale: He had chance to play 'a real superhero' and 'screwed it up'|work=The Hill|date=2019-01-09|access-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108011650/https://thehill.com/homenews/house/424492-liz-cheney-responds-to-christian-bale-calling-father-satan-he-had-the-chance|archive-date=2020-11-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾接下來在2019年運動劇情片《[[賽道狂人|賽道狂人]]》扮演賽車手[[肯·迈尔斯_(赛车运动员)|肯·邁爾斯]]，他在演完-{zh-hans:切尼;zh-hk:切尼;zh-tw:錢尼;}-後又為邁爾斯減了32公斤<ref name="done">{{cite web|last1=Desta|first1=Yohana|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2019/11/christian-bale-weight-loss|title=Christian Bale Swears He's Done Gaining and Losing Weight for Roles|work=Vanity Fair|date=2019-11-11|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029050629/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2019/11/christian-bale-weight-loss|archive-date=2020-10-29|url-status=live}}</ref>。影片由[[詹姆斯·曼高德|詹姆斯·曼高德]]執導，主要圍繞邁爾斯和汽車設計師[[卡洛·謝爾比|卡洛·謝爾比]]在{{tsl|en|1966 24 Hours of Le Mans|1966年勒芒24小時耐力賽}}發生的事情<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2019/11/14/779465165/matt-damon-on-playing-a-race-car-driver-in-famous-ford-ferrari-rivalry-of-the-60|title=Matt Damon On Playing A Race Car Driver in Famous Ford-Ferrari Rivalry Of The '60s|date=2019-11-14|access-date=2021-04-30|publisher=[[NPR|NPR]]|last=Kelly|first=Mary Louise|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220130224/https://www.npr.org/2019/11/14/779465165/matt-damon-on-playing-a-race-car-driver-in-famous-ford-ferrari-rivalry-of-the-60|archive-date=2019-12-20|url-status=live}}</ref>。該角讓貝爾五度入圍金球獎<ref name="fifth">{{cite web|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/thor-love-thunder-christian-bale-cast-1202822628/|title='Dark Knight' Star Christian Bale in Talks For Marvel's 'Thor: Love And Thunder'|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-01-06|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225231612/https://deadline.com/2020/01/thor-love-thunder-christian-bale-cast-1202822628/|archive-date=2021-02-25|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾跑電影宣傳時表示自己不再為角色作體重變動<ref name="done"/>。

貝爾打算在[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威電影宇宙]]超級英雄電影《[[雷神索爾：愛與雷霆|-{zh-tw:雷神索爾：愛與雷霆;zh-hk:雷神奇俠4：愛與雷霆;zh-cn:雷神4：爱与雷霆;}-]]》詮釋[[屠神者格爾|屠神者格爾]]，此片預計2022年7月上映<ref>{{Cite web|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2021/12/fandango-2022-movies-most-anticipated-black-panther-wakanda-forever-spider-verse-doctor-strange-2-1234901991/|title='Black Panther: Wakanda Forever', 'Spider-Man: Across The Spider-Verse' Among Most Anticipated 2022 Movies|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2021-12-27|access-date=2022-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211227174024/https://deadline.com/2021/12/fandango-2022-movies-most-anticipated-black-panther-wakanda-forever-spider-verse-doctor-strange-2-1234901991/|archive-date=2021-12-27|url-status=live}}</ref>。他也將參演-{zh-hans:大卫·欧·拉塞尔;zh-hk:大衛·奧·羅素;zh-tw:大衛·歐·羅素;}-的《[[坎特伯雷花窗|坎特伯雷花窗]]》和-{zh-hk:史葛·古巴;zh-tw:史考特·庫柏;zh-cn:斯科特·库珀;}-的驚悚片《{{tsl|en|The Pale Blue Eye|淡蓝眼眸}}》，兩片都是他和導演的第三次合作<ref name="third">{{Cite news |title=Christian Bale, David O. Russell in Talks to Team on New Regency Movie |first1=Dave|last1=McNary |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/christian-bale-david-o-russell-new-regency-movie-1203470136/ |work=Variety |date=2020-01-16|access-date=2020-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821044859/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/christian-bale-david-o-russell-new-regency-movie-1203470136/|archive-date=2020-08-21|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Wiseman|first1=Andreas|url=https://deadline.com/2021/03/netflix-christian-bale-pale-blue-eye-record-efm-deal-1234707264/|title=Netflix Strikes EFM Record $55M Worldwide Deal For Christian Bale Cross Creek Thriller 'The Pale Blue Eye'|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2021-03-06|access-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307051156/https://deadline.com/2021/03/netflix-christian-bale-pale-blue-eye-record-efm-deal-1234707264/|archive-date=2021-03-07|url-status=live}}</ref>，前者將於2022年11月上映<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kit|first=Borys|date=10 September 2021|title=Disney's Live-Action 'The Little Mermaid' to Open on Memorial Day Weekend in 2023|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/disneys-live-action-the-little-mermaid-memorial-day-weekend-opening-1235011622/|url-status=live|access-date=2022-02-04|website=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210910214925/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/disneys-live-action-the-little-mermaid-memorial-day-weekend-opening-1235011622/|archive-date=2021-09-10}}</ref>。貝爾即將在電影《铤而走险的教会》（{{lang|en|''The Church of Living Dangerously''}}）參與製作和出演牧師<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fleming|first1=Mike Jr|url=https://deadline.com/2021/08/christian-bale-the-church-of-living-dangerously-charles-randolph-new-regency-drug-dealing-preacher-john-lee-bishop-movie-deal-1234820186/|title=New Regency Acquires 'The Church Of Living Dangerously' For Christian Bale To Play Preacher On Hellish Drug Smuggling Road; Charles Randolph Scripting|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2021-08-23|access-date=2022-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220225063311/https://deadline.com/2021/08/christian-bale-the-church-of-living-dangerously-charles-randolph-new-regency-drug-dealing-preacher-john-lee-bishop-movie-deal-1234820186/|archive-date=2022-02-25|url-status=live}}</ref>。

==表演技巧與公眾形象==
貝爾以應戲份需要會無私改變體重，以及「他全情投入到徹底融入角色」而聞名<ref name="intensity"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Lattanzio|first1=Ryan|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/11/christian-bale-weight-gain-not-getting-fat-again-1202188459/|title=Christian Bale Says He's Done Getting Fat for Roles|publisher=IndieWire|date=2019-11-09|access-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225185648/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/11/christian-bale-weight-gain-not-getting-fat-again-1202188459/|archive-date=2021-02-25|url-status=live}}</ref>，《華盛頓郵報》的{{tsl|en|Ann Hornaday|安·霍納迪}}評價他根本是當代最有天賦的演員<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hornaday|first1=Ann|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/07/12/AR2007071202323.html|title='Rescue Dawn': A Light in War's Densest Jungle|work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]]|date=2007-07-13|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927052313/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/07/12/AR2007071202323.html|archive-date=2020-09-27|url-status=live}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|RogerEbert.com}}》的馬克斯·奧康奈爾（{{lang|en|Max O'Connell}}）認為貝爾在演出時全力改變外貌是「描繪癡迷的錨定刻面」<ref>{{cite web|last1=O'Connell|first1=Max|url=https://www.rogerebert.com/features/obsession-and-the-void-the-performances-of-christian-bale|title=Obsession and The Void: The Performances of Christian Bale|work=RogerEbert.com|date=2019-01-14|access-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204151131/https://www.rogerebert.com/features/obsession-and-the-void-the-performances-of-christian-bale|archive-date=2020-12-04|url-status=live}}</ref>，而《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的休·哈特（{{lang|en|Hugh Hart}}）將主導貝爾表演風格的緊迫感比作[[方法演技|方法演技]]，並補充這「有力到甚至激發了他最極端的身體變化」<ref name="vicetransformation"/>。貝爾曾表示自己從未用過方法演技，也沒採取任何特定技巧<ref>{{cite web|url=https://apnews.com/article/8d0112708eef4c9e940aa40084ed2809|title=Christian Bale 'wings it' on set|publisher=[[美聯社|Associated Press]]|date=2018-12-28|access-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429193926/https://apnews.com/article/8d0112708eef4c9e940aa40084ed2809|archive-date=2021-04-29|url-status=live}}</ref>。他稱羅溫·艾金森是自己作為演員的模板，原因是兩人合作時被-{zh-cn:艾金森; zh-tw:艾金森; zh-hk:雅堅遜;}-完全迷住<ref>{{cite web|last1=McGurk|first1=Stuart|url=https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/culture/article/matt-damon-christian-bale-ford-v-ferrari-interview|title=Matt Damon and Christian Bale interview: When Bourne met Batman|work=British GQ|date=2019-10-01|access-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128050626/https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/culture/article/matt-damon-christian-bale-ford-v-ferrari-interview|archive-date=2021-01-28|url-status=live}}</ref>。他還學習了[[加里·奧德曼|-{zh-hans:加里·奥德曼; zh-hk:加利·奧文; zh-tw:蓋瑞·歐德曼;}-]]的作品，認為-{zh-hans:奥德曼; zh-hk:奧文; zh-tw:歐德曼;}-是他追求表演的原因<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thequint.com/entertainment/cinema/christian-bale-interview-mowgli-bagheera-netflix-performance-capture-technology-physical-transformation|title=Christian Bale Says He's Almost Done With Physical Transformations|last=Mathew|first=Suresh|date=2018-11-26|website=The Quint|access-date=2018-11-30|archive-date=2018-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130202006/https://www.thequint.com/entertainment/cinema/christian-bale-interview-mowgli-bagheera-netflix-performance-capture-technology-physical-transformation|url-status=live}}</ref>。

貝爾的多變也取得認可<ref name="teeth"/><ref name="variety"/>，《[[聖荷西信使報|聖荷西信使報]]》的瑪莎·羅斯（{{lang|en|Martha Ross}}）稱他是當代最多才多藝的演員<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ross|first1=Martha|url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2017/04/13/christian-bale-goes-from-american-psycho-to-dick-cheney-with-new-role/|title=Christian Bale goes from 'American Psycho' to Dick Cheney with new role|work=[[聖荷西信使報|The Mercury News]]|date=2017-04-13|access-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203064814/https://www.mercurynews.com/2017/04/13/christian-bale-goes-from-american-psycho-to-dick-cheney-with-new-role/|archive-date=2018-12-03|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾對自己的私人生活十分保密，曾表示想達到在不展示自己任何方面的情況下來體現整個人<ref>{{cite web|last1=Marchese|first1=David|url=https://www.vulture.com/2014/12/christian-bale-is-our-least-relatable-movie-star.html|title=Christian Bale Is Our Least Relatable Movie Star|website=Vulture|url-access=limited|date=12 December 2014|access-date=30 April 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204235443/https://www.vulture.com/2014/12/christian-bale-is-our-least-relatable-movie-star.html|archive-date=4 December 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>，並解釋「讓別人知道你是誰」無助於創造不同角色，更認為不公開「能讓你扮演好這些角色」<ref name="thr"/>。貝爾跑宣傳接受訪問時，如果是帶有口音的電影，他就會用特定的腔調講話<ref name="spy">{{cite web|last1=Hilton|first1=Beth|url=https://www.digitalspy.com/showbiz/10-things-about/a105893/ten-things-you-never-knew-about-christian-bale/|title=Ten Things You Never Knew About Christian Bale|publisher=Digital Spy|date=2008-07-02|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603063028/https://www.digitalspy.com/showbiz/10-things-about/a105893/ten-things-you-never-knew-about-christian-bale/|archive-date=2020-06-03|url-status=live}}</ref>，甚至因詮釋美國口音的角色而聞名<ref>{{cite web|last1=Stolworthy|first1=Jacob|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/christian-bale-accent-cockney-where-voice-matt-damon-le-mans-66-ford-ferrari-a9202486.html|title=Christian Bale's accent confuses British television viewers: 'It's weird hearing him speak in his real voice'|website=The Independent|date=2019-11-14|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114133859/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/christian-bale-accent-cockney-where-voice-matt-damon-le-mans-66-ford-ferrari-a9202486.html|archive-date=2019-11-14|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Reid|first1=Joe|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2013/12/christian-bale-and-actors-who-work-least-their-native-accents/355879/|title=Christian Bale and the Actors Who Work Least in Their Native Accents|work=The Atlantic|date=2013-12-06|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815204611/https://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2013/12/christian-bale-and-actors-who-work-least-their-native-accents/355879/|archive-date=2020-08-15|url-status=live}}</ref>，而貝爾在真實生活中講著一口「有力、不時髦的」英國口音<ref name="first"/>。

2011年，貝爾入選《[[時代雜誌|時代]]》年度世界[[時代百大人物|最具影響力的百大人物]]<ref>{{cite magazine|title=The 2011 TIME 100 Poll|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2058044_2060338_2059896,00.html|date=2011-04-04|access-date=2016-01-29|magazine=[[時代雜誌|Time]]|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130005050/https://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2058044_2060338_2059896,00.html|url-status=live}}</ref>。三年後，他以3500萬美元在《[[福布斯|-{zh-cn:福布斯; zh-sg:资本家杂志; zh-hk:福布斯; zh-tw:富比士;}-]]》最高收入演員的名單中排名第九<ref>{{cite web|last1=Child|first1=Ben|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/jul/22/robert-downey-jr-forbes-highest-earning|title=Robert Downey Jr tops list of highest paid actors for second year running|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2014-07-22|access-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210526103051/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/jul/22/robert-downey-jr-forbes-highest-earning|archive-date=2021-05-26|url-status=live}}</ref>。貝爾也被視為[[性感象徵|性感符號]]<ref name="masked"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Robinson|first1=Tasha|url=https://www.avclub.com/a-filmgoers-guide-to-bad-sex-with-christian-bale-1798212606|title= A filmgoer's guide to bad sex with Christian Bale|website=[[影音俱樂部|The A.V. Club]]|date=2007-10-16|access-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703140445/https://www.avclub.com/a-filmgoers-guide-to-bad-sex-with-christian-bale-1798212606|archive-date=2020-07-03|url-status=live}}</ref>。

==私人生活==
[[File:Christian_Bale_and_Sibi_Blažić_Berlinale_2019.jpg|thumb]]]]
貝爾從1990年代開始就住在洛杉磯<ref name="first"/>，並持有美國國籍<ref name="citizenship"/><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.esquire.com/uk/culture/film/news/a7424/christian-bale-interview/|title=Christian Bale: The Full Shoot And Interview|date=2014-12-10|work=Esquire|access-date=2018-02-17|archive-date=2019-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190108041909/https://www.esquire.com/uk/culture/film/news/a7424/christian-bale-interview/|url-status=live}}</ref>。2000年1月29日，貝爾與前模特桑德拉·「西碧」·布拉齊克（{{lang|en|Sandra "Sibi" Blažić}}）在洛杉磯喜結連理<ref name="spy"/><ref name="personal">{{Cite web|url=https://people.com/movies/christian-bale-wife-sibi-blazic-celebrate-19th-wedding-anniversary-bike-ride/|title=Christian Bale and Wife Enjoy Bike Ride on 19th Wedding Anniversary – Day Before His Birthday!|date=2019-01-30|access-date=2021-04-30|website=People|last=Russian|first=Ale|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814075022/https://people.com/movies/christian-bale-wife-sibi-blazic-celebrate-19th-wedding-anniversary-bike-ride/|archive-date=2020-08-14|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity/a25935496/christian-bale-wife-sibi-blazic/|title=Who Is Christian Bale's Wife Sibi Blazic? The Model Changed Everything for the Actor|date=2019-01-17|access-date=2021-04-30|website=Marie Claire|last=Mitchell|first=Amanda|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206062407/https://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity/a25935496/christian-bale-wife-sibi-blazic/|archive-date=2021-02-06|url-status=live}}</ref>，兩人育有一兒一女<ref name="personal"/>。2000年，貝爾成為女權主義者[[格洛丽亚·斯泰纳姆|格洛丽亚·斯泰纳姆]]的繼子，而父親三年後死於{{tsl|en|Primary central nervous system lymphoma|原發性中樞神經系統淋巴瘤|顱內淋巴瘤}}<ref>{{cite news|last = von Zeilbauer|first = Paul|title = David Bale, 62, Activist and businessman|work = [[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|date = 2004-01-01|url = https://www.nytimes.com/2004/01/01/us/david-bale-62-activist-and-businessman.html|access-date = 2014-11-16|url-status=live|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141111173509/https://www.nytimes.com/2004/01/01/us/david-bale-62-activist-and-businessman.html|archive-date = 2014-11-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Denes|first1=Melissa|title='Feminism? It's hardly begun'|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2005/jan/17/gender.melissadenes|access-date=2014-12-23|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2005-01-16|archive-date=2017-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731225927/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2005/jan/17/gender.melissadenes|url-status=live}}</ref>。

貝爾在7歲時成為[[素食主義|素食主義者]]，卻在2009年稱他「現在（只是）素食主義的常客」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gq.com/story/christian-bale-batman-john-connor-terminator|title=A Nice Quiet Chat with Christian Bale|date=2009-05-01|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[GQ|GQ]]|last=Corsello|first=Andrew|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030343/https://www.gq.com/story/christian-bale-batman-john-connor-terminator|archive-date=12 November 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>，並在讀完兒童文物《[[夏洛特的网|-{zh-hant:夏綠蒂的網; zh-hans:夏洛特的网;}-]]》後不再吃[[紅肉|紅肉]]<ref name="spy"/>。他作為動物權益活動家，有支持[[綠色和平|綠色和平]]、[[世界自然基金會|世界自然基金會]]、{{tsl|en|Doris Day Animal League|桃樂絲·黛動物聯盟|-{zh-hans:多丽丝·戴;zh-hant:桃樂絲·黛;zh-hk:桃麗絲·黛}-動物聯盟}}、{{tsl|en|Dian Fossey Gorilla Fund International|黛安·佛西大猩猩基金會|-{zh-cn:戴安·弗西; zh-tw:黛安·佛西; zh-hk:戴安·弗西}-大猩猩基金會}}和{{tsl|en|Redwings Horse Sanctuary|紅翼馬庇護所}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2000-apr-13-ca-18918-story.html|title=Bale's 'Psycho' Analysis|date=2000-04-13|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|url-access=limited|last=Jan|first=Stuart|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430040906/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2000-apr-13-ca-18918-story.html|archive-date=2021-04-30|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/1999/jun/20/comment.nickpatonwalsh|title=Christian Bale|date=1999-06-20|access-date=2021-04-30|website=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|last=Walsh|first=Nick Paton|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191001085950/https://www.theguardian.com/film/1999/jun/20/comment.nickpatonwalsh|archive-date=2019-10-01|url-status=live}}</ref>。2011年12月，貝爾在宣傳《金陵十三釵》期間，與[[有線電視新聞網|有線電視新聞網]]的工作人員嘗試探望軟禁在中國東部農村的盲人赤腳律師[[陳光誠|陳光誠]]，但在檢查站與警衛發生衝突後被迫遣返<ref name="CNN1512">{{cite web|last1=Jiang|first1=Steven|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2011/12/15/world/asia/china-bale-activist/index.html|title='Batman' star Bale punched, stopped from visiting blind Chinese activist|date=2011-12-17|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|access-date=2012-04-27|archive-date=2011-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111216005838/https://edition.cnn.com/2011/12/15/world/asia/china-bale-activist/index.html|url-status=live}}</ref>，直到隔年在非營利組織{{tsl|en|Human Rights First|人权第一}}舉辦的晚宴才見到陳光誠，期間貝爾頒獎給他<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-CJB-16704|title=Chen Guangcheng Honored by Human Rights First, Meets Bale|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2012-10-25|access-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210708174459/https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-CJB-16704|archive-date=2021-07-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。之後貝爾在[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]的-{zh-cn:播客; zh-tw:podcast; zh-hk:podcast}-《用他們自己的話說》（{{lang|en|''In Their Own Words''}}）講述陳光誠的故事<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sturges|first1=Fiona|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/their-own-words-podcast-review-christian-bale-outshone-human-rights-champion-a6852166.html|title=In Their Own Words, podcast review: Christian Bale is outshone by a human rights champion|work=The Independent|date=2016-02-03|access-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225195618/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/their-own-words-podcast-review-christian-bale-outshone-human-rights-champion-a6852166.html|archive-date=2021-02-25|url-status=live}}</ref>。

2008年7月22日，貝爾在倫敦被捕，原因是母親和姐姐莎朗向警方報案他涉嫌襲擊，之後被[[保釋|保釋]]出獄<ref name="darkallegation"/>。貝爾否認所有指控，並稱這是「非常私人的事情」<ref name="masked"/>。8月14日，[[英格蘭及威爾斯皇家檢控署|英格蘭及威爾斯皇家檢控署]]宣布因「證據不足無法提供實質的定罪機會」而不會對他採取進一步的行動<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7561844.stm|title=No assault charge for Batman Bale|access-date=2009-02-06|date=2008-08-14|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227035537/https://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7561844.stm|url-status=live}}</ref>。

==演出作品與所獲榮譽==
{{main|克里斯汀·貝爾作品列表|克里斯汀·貝爾獲獎與提名列表}}
[[匯總媒體|匯總媒體]]網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據收到的正面評價數量為電影打分，貝爾評分最高的作品《黑暗騎士》、《賽道狂人》、《美国骗局》、《-{zh-tw:新小婦人; zh-hk:小婦人; zh-hans:小妇人;}-》、《-{zh-hans:斗士; zh-tw:燃燒鬥魂; zh-hk:擊情手足;}-》、《重見天日》、《决斗犹马镇》、《-{zh-tw:大賣空;zh-cn:大空头;zh-hk:沽注一擲;}-》、《霍爾的移動城堡》和《黑暗騎士：黎明昇起》，而首部、第三部和最後一部影片與《魔鬼終結者：未來救贖》、《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》、《风中奇缘》和《出埃及記：天地王者》在數據網站[[The_Numbers|The Numbers]]列為他票房最高的電影<ref>{{cite web|url=https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/all-christian-bale-movies-ranked/|title=All Christian Bale Movies Ranked|publisher=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]|access-date=2021-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206175615/https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/all-christian-bale-movies-ranked/|archive-date=2021-02-06|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.the-numbers.com/person/9490401-Christian-Bale#tab=acting&all_acting_credits=od5|title=Christian Bale – Box Office|publisher=[[The_Numbers|The Numbers]]|access-date=2021-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402005216/https://www.the-numbers.com/person/9490401-Christian-Bale#tab=acting&all_acting_credits=od5|archive-date=2021-04-02|url-status=live}}</ref>。

貝爾入圍四項奧斯卡金像獎，憑藉《美国骗局》和《為副不仁》提名[[奧斯卡最佳男主角獎|最佳男主角]]，並以《燃燒鬥魂》和《-{zh-tw:大賣空;zh-cn:大空头;zh-hk:沽注一擲;}-》提名[[奧斯卡最佳男配角獎|最佳男配角]]，最後以《燃燒鬥魂》拿下寶座<ref>{{cite web|last1=Roeper|first1=Richard|url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/2019/11/11/20956417/christian-bale-ford-v-ferrari-ken-miles-interview-accent|title=Christian Bale says his 'Ford v Ferrari' ride beats the Batmobile|work=Chicago Sun-Times|date=2019-11-11|access-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111161322/https://chicago.suntimes.com/2019/11/11/20956417/christian-bale-ford-v-ferrari-ken-miles-interview-accent|archive-date=2019-11-11|url-status=live}}</ref>。他拿下兩座金球獎，分別憑《燃燒鬥魂》和《為副不仁》奪得最佳電影男配角和最佳音樂及喜劇類電影男主角，而他也以《美国骗局》和《-{zh-tw:大賣空;zh-cn:大空头;zh-hk:沽注一擲;}-》入圍最佳電影男配角，更以《賽道狂人》入圍[[金球獎劇情類電影最佳男主角|劇情類電影最佳男主角]]<ref name="screendaily"/><ref name="fifth"/>。貝爾還入圍八座[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Turan|first1=Kenneth|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-01-16/performances-christian-bale-ford-v-ferrari|title=Performances we love: Christian Bale fools us again|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|url-access=limited|date=2020-01-16|access-date=2021-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120020743/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-01-16/performances-christian-bale-ford-v-ferrari|archive-date=2021-01-20|url-status=live}}</ref>，以《燃燒鬥魂》贏得[[美國演員工會獎最佳男配角|最佳男配角]]，並以出演《美国骗局》拿下{{tsl|en|Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture|美國演員工會獎最佳整體演出|最佳整體演出}}<ref>{{cite web|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|last2=Powers|first2=Lindsay|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/sag-awards-2011-christian-bale-94503/|title=SAG Awards 2011: Christian Bale Surprised On Stage by Dicky Eklund|website=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2011-01-30|access-date=2021-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210910045922/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/sag-awards-2011-christian-bale-94503/|archive-date=2021-09-10|url-s